18.18: “+‘meib Eei auq Zxg zyavb Jyenq Eei zyavb hog, maiq tuvq cvj lovg ninb Eei txg fai Riad zruj aub Rcvb pwav yaag Zauj ninb pweij.
18.8: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij meib Eei tia Eei auq. Navq naaiq zyrug paaig zu'g tia.
18.3: meib Bua maiq tuvq zruj Navq ninb Bua yem i-yipq teib puv zruj uaq nx, tovb zinb Daavg meib Bua yem uaq nxm teib puv. yaag maiq tuvq zruj Navq ninb Bua yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv zruj Eei, tovb yia ib zang txb Jyenq meib Bua Tauj Eei teib puv. uaq teij myenb zruj Eei, meib Bua maiq tuvq zwrtg Jyenq zruj.
18.21: “+‘maiq tuvq zx'q meib Bua Eei haiq taub fu'Jweiq lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun mo-lekq zyenb. naaiq se mavg Piaj, paaig zu'g meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei Buaj. yia se zyruq.
18.14: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij meib pc'g tiaj Eei auq fai yrub tiaj Eei auq weig zu'g ninb Bua zruj meib Eei Juab Zauj meib Eei Riab maag.
18.23: “+‘maiq tuvq Yenj scvb Kuq, pun kanb maaib wij. msia'q txn yaag maiq tuvq txb kanb pun scvb Kuq scv. naaiq se zruj maiq lwrnj hxvg Eei sig.
18.6: “+‘haiq taub maiq tuvq mivb Zauj Jwavg Ryaamb fei Eei Zyenb Ze'q nitq txig. yia se zyruq.
18.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
18.20: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij myenb Eei auq. Navq naaiq zyrug kua'q zu'g kanb maaib wij.
18.24: “+‘meib Bua maiq tuvq zruj naaiq teij yetg zuvq sig pun kanb maaib wij, weig zu'g yia xij zung Zwrtq meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj uaq teij fivb fivj myenb zruj naaiq teij sig pun kanb maaib wij.
18.28: sij kxvq meib Bua pun teib puv maaib wij, teib puv zyrug loq meib Bua Zwrtq Navq loq yem Daavg meib Bua uaq teij fivb fivj myenb nx.
18.7: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij kanb Eei maa. ninb zruj meib Eei maa, maiq tuvq pweij. Navq naaiq paaig zu'g meib Eei tia.
18.29: “+‘haiq taub zruj naaiq teij haiq Euvg kamb Riaq Eei sig, uaq taub yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zuvq zu'g Pai kwavg.
18.19: “+‘msia'q txn sinb yeng, maaib wij Eei zyavb hog, maiq tuvq pweij.
18.17: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij haiq taub msia'q txn cvj lyemb ninb Eei sia'q pweij. yaag maiq tuvq pweij ninb Eei txn Eei sia'q fai sia'q Eei sia'q. ninb Bua se Zauj uaq taub msia'q txn Jwavg Ryaamb fei Eei Zyenb Ze'q. Navq naaiq zruj se zruj waaig sig.
18.30: xij zu'g ei Jyenq yia Paaiq Eei waag zruj yaag maiq tuvq zwrtg yem Daavg meib Bua uaq teij kamb Riaq haig Eei leid. yaag maiq tuvq pun kanb laaij naaiq teij sig maaib wij. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.’+”
18.27: yem uaq nxm teib puv Daavg meib Bua uaq teij myenb zruj naaiq teij sig, teib puv zyrug maaib wij.
18.11: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij tia Eei auq Eei sia'q, se Jwavg tia maiq Jwavg maa Eei sia'q. ninb zruj meib Eei txg fai muag.
18.5: weig naaiq meib Bua xij zu'g mwavj lovj yia Eei livg, kan lovj yia Eei leid. myenb ei Jyenq zruj zyrug tu'q zyavb Jyenq. yia se zyruq.
18.9: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij kanb Eei txg fai muag, maiq kunq tia Eei sia'q fai maa Eei sia'q, Jwavg pyauq Zwrtq seij fai yem kanb nxm txvj Zwrtq seij Eei.
18.16: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij kanb Eei muab txig Eei auq. Navq naaiq zruj paaig zu'g meib Eei kxj fai yrud.
18.4: meib Bua xij zu'g kan yia Eei leid, mwavj lovj yia Eei livg yaag ei Jyenq zruj. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
18.10: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij meib Eei fun, maiq kunq txn Eei sia'q fai sia'q Eei sia'q. naaiq se paaig zu'g meib kanb.
18.22: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij mJavg txn txvj msia'q txn. se kamb Riaq haig Eei sig.
18.12: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij meib Eei krub maag fai muab maag. ninb se Zauj meib Eei tia Jwavg Ryaamb fei Eei Zyenb Ze'q.
18.15: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij kanb Eei Bwavd. ninb zruj meib Eei txn Eei auq. maiq tuvq pweij ninb.
18.13: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij meib Eei txg teib fai Riab maag. ninb se Zauj meib Eei maa Jwavg Ryaamb fei Eei Zyenb Ze'q.
18.26: mq paag meib Bua xij zu'g ei Revg yia Eei livg Zauj yia Eei leid. maiq kunq pwrnb fivj myenb fai yem meib Bua ka'Euad Eei kanb fivj myenb, maiq tuvq zruj naaiq teij haiq Euvg kamb Riaq Eei sig.
18.25: lyemb teib puv yaag maaib wij. yia zyrug tivg teib puv Eei zwid. teib puv zyrug loq Zwrtq yem Jyenq Eei pc'g fivj.

8.18: ninb cvj zx'q weig puaq ziag Eei pa'ki yuvb kruq taaib. aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua txb puad maan Jyenq naaiq taub pa'ki yuvb Eei mGxvq.
8.8: mo-se cvj zx'q pwav la'Kwrtq uaq Kwaaiq ka'naaiq pwav Jyenq aa-lon Eei la'Kwrtq, yaag zx'q u-lim Zauj Tum-mim tapq Jyenq ka'Euad,
8.33: xij zu'g yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg siag Nxi yaag maiq tuvq Zwrtq mivb haiq Dau. zuaq Tauj xn zruj sai myenb Eei leid Eei Nxib Eia'g pwavq, weig zu'g xn myenb Eei leid se lovg siag Nxi Zivj tunb yunb.
8.3: cvj heug zwavj pc'g fivj taaib kapq zunq yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg.”
8.32: zevg Fiag Eei xq Zauj Fuaq xij zu'g lovg trud puaq kwavg.
8.21: lovg uam Raauj liud ka'Euad Hruq Eei ka'naaiq Zauj zwib, mo-se zyrug zx'q naaiq taub pa'ki yuvb Eei Euvb Euvg an ziab txvb puaq ziag, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq. se lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq, ziuj zyruq Buaj mo-se zruj uaq nx.
8.35: xij zu'g yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg pwavq siag Nxi siag mwrnd, ei Jyenq zyruq Eei waag zruj. maiq zei c'q, Riaj meib Bua zu'g taig weig zu'g zyruq Navq naaiq nx hatg yia.”
8.14: mo-se zx'q ziag weig fi'q zwid uaq taub vovb kruq taaib. aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua zyrug txb puad maan Jyenq vovb Eei mGxvq.
8.23: mo-se zyrug taij taaib cvj zx'q teij pa'ki yuvb Eei Ryaamq kua'q aa-lon Eei Byaaug puv mnxmb pyruq Zauj Byaaug Jia'q puab Do'g Eeid Zauj Byaaug Jia'q zaub Do'g Eeid.
8.6: mo-se zyrug txb aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua taaib, lovg uam Tevj ninb Bua Raauj sin.
8.34: ib Nxi zruj Eei se ziuj zyruq Buaj Eei waag weig Tevj meib Bua fi'q zwid.
8.2: “txb aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua taaib sruq Jyenq wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg. cvj txb zruj sai Eei lwib hruj Zauj xn myenb Eei yrub Zauj taub vovb kruq ziag fi'q zwid Zauj i taub pa'ki yuvb kruq, Zauj Daan maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq taaib.
8.36: aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua zyrug ei Jyenq zyruq lovg mo-se Paaiq Eei waag zruj Revg.
8.20: Va'q pa'ki yuvb penj yetg Ganj yetg Ganj liud, mo-se zx'q mGxvq Zauj xq, lyemb Mei puaq Revg.
8.24: zruj liud, zyrug txb aa-lon Eei txn Bua taaib cvj zx'q teij naaiq taub yuvb Eei Ryaamq kua'q ninb Bua Eei Byaaug puv mnxmb pyruq, Byaaug Jia'q puab Do'g Eeid Zauj Byaaug Jia'q zaub Do'g Eeid. zevg Fiag Eei Ryaamq mo-se Pyetq ziab txvb pyei puv.
8.28: mo-se cvj zx'q yem ninb Bua Eei puad uaq teij ka'naaiq taaib an Jyenq ziab txvb, puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq kub vwaaig, yetg Fiag puaq. se ziag weig xn myenb zruj sai myenb Eei ka'naaiq, lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
8.7: ninb zx'q ka'Euad uaq yemg lwib Daauq Tevj aa-lon zu'q Jyenq, sai Jyenq Jiaj Jaaiq Dia. zx'q tomb lwib kwaaj Tevj ninb zu'q Jyenq. cvj zx'q e-fotq pun ninb zu'q Jyenq, yaag lovg puab taub lovj, Datq taaib Rweig Eei e-fotq Laav, sai Jyenq sin lovj Eei.
8.29: mo-se yaag zx'q lx'g Ywav xq yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Zunq kiv weig zruj Zunq kiv fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. naaiq se mo-se Eei pwrng lovg xn myenb zruj sai myenb Eei yuvb kruq xq, ziuj zyruq Paaiq mo-se Eei waag.
8.19: mo-se zyrug taij taaib, zx'q pa'ki yuvb Eei Ryaamq Pyetq Wiv kxmj ziab txvb pyei puv.
8.17: mq paag vovb Eei Dopq Zauj xq Zauj Jaavb txb Zwrtq zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq lovg trud puaq kwavg, ziuj zyruq Buaj mo-se Eei waag zruj.
8.31: mo-se Buaj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua, “zx'q xq yem uaq wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg zruq, yaag yem uaq Eang, Zauj Jyenq fovg hxg weig xn zruj sai myenb uaq nxm Daan Eei Fuaq Navq yia Paaiq zyavj kxvq, ‘naaiq se aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua xij zu'g Eang.’
8.30: mo-se cvj zx'q teij xn myenb Eei yrub Zauj yem ziab txvb Eei Ryaamq fu'q aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei lwib hruj. yaag fu'q aa-lon Eei txn Bua Zauj ninb Bua Eei lwib hruj. Navq naaig ninb zx'q aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua Zauj ninb Bua zruj sai Eei lwib hruj fuvj pun zyruq.
8.27: naaiq teij ka'naaiq yetg zuvq ninb Yetq Jyenq aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua Eei puad. ninb Bua zyrug yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Zunq kiv weig zruj Zunq kiv fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq.
8.11: ninb cvj lovg uaq teij yrub fu'q ziab txvb kub vwaaig siag Rung, yaag kua'q ziag txvb Zauj ziab txvb Eei yetg zuvq Jaab sig Zauj punb Zauj punb Eei Taapq weig saaj Zivb Revg taaib.
8.5: mo-se Buaj zwavj myenb, “zyruq Paaiq zyavj xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx zruj.”
8.9: zx'q mGxvb peu peu Jyenq ninb Eei mGxvq. cvj zx'q zruj Javb hog piuj mevb fuvj pun zyruq uaq Kwaaiq Jyemb paaib nctq Jyenq mGxvb peu Ra'Myen mcvj.
8.16: mo-se zx'q yetg zuvq yem Hruq Eei Mei, pwav Jyenq Lan Eei xb Byxvd, i nxm Eutg zeiq Zauj nctq Eutg zeiq Eei Mei, an Jyenq ziab txvb kub vwaaig puaq.
8.4: mo-se ziuj zyruq Buaj Eei waag zruj Revg. zwavj myenb zyrug taaib kapq zunq yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg.
8.10: mo-se zyrug lovg xn myenb Eei yrub toj zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub Zauj yem Dopg liub Eei Euvb Euvg ka'naaiq, zx'q yetg zuvq fuvj penj zyruq Eei.
8.22: mo-se cvj zx'q ta'Eeig taub pa'ki yuvb kruq, tovb lovg xn myenb zruj sai myenb uaq taub. aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua txb puad maan Jyenq uaq taub pa'ki yuvb kruq Eei mGxvq.
8.12: ninb cvj lovg xn myenb Eei yrub toj aa-lon Eei mGxvq weig xn ninb yaag saaj ninb Zivb Revg.
8.15: mo-se zyrug taij uaq taub vovb, lovg puab Do'q Zo'q vovb Eei Ryaamq zaij ziab txvb pyei nxm kx'q Eei Jxv weig pun ziab txvb Zivb Revg. ninb zx'q Ryaamq toj Fiag ziab txvb Eei kxn weig saaj ziab txvb Eei wij, zx'q ziab txvb fuvj pun zyruq.
8.13: mo-se cvj txb aa-lon Eei txn Bua taaib Tevj ninb Bua zu'q lwib Daauq, sai Jyenq Jiaj Jaaiq Dia, zx'q muag pun ninb Dovj Jyenq, ziuj zyruq Buaj mo-se nx.
8.26: yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen uaq Daan maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq mo-se zx'q nxm maiq an pivq zxpg Jyenq ka'lanq yrub Eei Fuaq, Zauj yetg nxm Raatq Jyenq ka'lanq yrub Eei Fuaq Zauj yetg nxm Fuab pia'g Yetq Jyenq Mei Zauj Byaaug puv zaub zwib kub vwaaig.
8.25: ninb cvj zx'q Mei Zauj Jung Eei tweiq, lyemb yetg zuvq yem Hruq Eei Mei, Zauj pwav Jyenq Lan Eei xb Byxvd, i nxm Eutg zeiq Zauj panq yrub Zauj Byaaug puv zaub zwib.

3.3: yem naaiq teij ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq, ninb xij zu'g zx'q teij lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq. xij zu'g zx'q yem Hruq Eei Mei Zauj yetg zuvq Zc'g Jaavb Mei,
3.8: xij zu'g txb puad maan Jyenq ninb ziag uaq taub scvb Kuq Eei mGxvq, yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg taij. aa-lon Eei txn Bua zyrug zx'q Ryaamq Pyetq Wiv kxmj ziab txvb pyei puv.
3.9: yem naaiq teij ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq xij zu'g txb teij lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq. xij zu'g txb yetg zuvq Mei, Jung Eei tweiq kaatq Tauj kxn, kaatq Tauj ti'g taand mweib Buvq, Zauj yetg zuvq yem Hruq Eei Mei, lyemb Zc'g Jaavb Mei,
3.7: ninb lovg taub pa'ki yuvb txn ziag nx, xij zu'g txb mivb yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen.
3.5: aa-lon Eei txn zyrug zx'q naaiq pua'q ka'naaiq an ziab txvb, puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq kub vwaaig. puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq yem zia'g Jyenq trud Eei zaavb kub vwaaig. naaiq se lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
3.16: sai myenb zyrug an ziab txvb kub vwaaig lovg trud puaq ziag zruj Eang Eei ka'naaiq fovg hxg pun zyruq weib Daav Eei Qiaj. Mei yetg zuvq penj zyruq Eei.
3.17: “+‘maiq kunq meib Bua yem haaij, maiq tuvq Eang Mei fai Ryaamq. naaiq se meib Bua txig Jiaj txig, yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid.’+”
3.14: yem ninb fovg hxg Eei yuvb xij zu'g zx'q teij lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq. xij zu'g zx'q yetg zuvq yem Hruq Eei Mei, lyemb Zc'g Jaavb Mei,
3.4: Zauj i nxm Eutg zeiq, Zauj nctq Eutg zeiq Eei panq yrub. pwav Jyenq Lan Eei xb Byxvd yaag xij zu'g Zauj Eutg zeiq zx'q Zwrtq.
3.2: xij zu'g txb puad maan Jyenq ninb ziag uaq taub scvb Kuq Eei mGxvq, yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg taij. aa-lon Eei txn, sai myenb Bua, zyrug zx'q Ryaamq taaib Pyetq Wiv kxmj ziab txvb pyei puv.
3.6: “+‘sij kxvq txb yem pa'ki yuvb fai yuvb kwanb Eei scvb Kuq taaib ziag pun zyruq weig Jiu Tov, xij zu'g txb maiq waaig favj Eei pa'ki yuvb fai yuvb, maiq kunq kruq fai Eeid.
3.13: xij zu'g txb puad maan Jyenq yuvb Eei mGxvq, yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg taij. aa-lon Eei txn Bua zyrug zx'q Ryaamq Pyetq ziab txvb pyei puv.
3.12: “+‘sij kxvq myenb ziag Eei ka'naaiq se yuvb, xij zu'g txb taaib yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen fovg hxg.
3.15: i nxm Eutg zeiq Zauj nctq Eutg zeiq Eei panq yrub. pwav Jyenq Lan Eei xb Byxvd yaag xij zu'g Zauj Jyenq Eutg zeiq zx'q Zwrtq.
3.11: sai myenb zyrug an ziab txvb kub vwaaig lovg trud puaq ziag zruj Eang Eei ka'naaiq fovg hxg pun zyruq.
3.1: “+‘sij kxvq myenb fovg hxg ka'naaiq ziag weig Jiu Tov, ninb yaag lovg yem vovb kwanb zx'q Zwrtq taaib Eei, maiq kunq vovb kruq fai Eeid, xij zu'g yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen fovg hxg maiq waaig favj Eei scvb Kuq.
3.10: i nxm Eutg zeiq Zauj nctq Eutg zeiq Eei panq yrub. pwav Jyenq Lan Eei xb Byxvd yaag xij zu'g Zauj Jyenq Eutg zeiq zx'q Zwrtq.

21.18: ta'faanb waaig favj Eei myenb maiq tu'q taaib fatq. se mziv mcvb Eei, fai zauj Bai Eei, Myen waaig favj Eei, sin zavg waaig favj Eei,
21.8: xij zu'g funj ninb Bua Zivb Revg weig zu'g ninb Bua fovg hxg meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei Eang hopq. xij zu'g funj ninb Bua Zivb Revg, weig zu'g yia, zyruq, tovb pun meib Bua Zivb Revg uaq taub, se Zivb Revg.
21.3: fai maiq Zwrtq kcvb Eei txg fai muag. txg fai muag maiq maaib Goj zyrug weig ninb zu'g maaib wij tu'q Eei.
21.21: aa-lon sai myenb Eei zeib fun, ta'faanb haiq taub waaig favj Eei, maiq haib taaib fatq fovg hxg lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei ka'naaiq. laaij ninb waaig favj, maiq haib taaib fatq fovg hxg ninb Eei Tinb huvb Eei Eang hopq.
21.14: maiq tuvq lovg aub kwaaq, aub leib, fai Ryaaug Jiaj txn Eei sia'q fai maaig pwrnb sin Eei msia'q txn. Kuvj lovg kanb Eei pc'g fivj, maiq pweij Jiaj txn Eei sia'q, zruj auq Navq.
21.23: mq paag laaij ninb Eei sin zavg waaig, ninb maiq haib Tauj fatq sivj ting Eei Bc'g kcvb Dia fai ziab txvb, pun yia Eei sivj ting maaib wij. yia se zyruq, tovb pun ninb Bua Zivb Revg uaq taub.’+”
21.6: ninb Bua xij zu'g Zivb Revg weig ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yaag maiq tuvq paaig ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei Buaj. ninb Bua xij zu'g Zivb Revg weig zu'g ninb Bua zx'q lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq pun zyruq, se ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei Eang hopq.
21.2: Zwrtq liud weig kaub Zyen Jiaj uaq teij. se weig kanb Eei tiaj maag, txn fai sia'q, kxj fai yrud,
21.20: Jaaiq Bruq Eei, Eanq Eei, mziv waaig Eei, maaib Dopq huq, putq faav Eei pcvg, fai Jaib Dwib vanb waaig Eei.
21.24: mo-se zyrug kxvq Revg naaiq teij Jaub lrug Buaj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Zauj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb.
21.7: “+‘sai myenb maiq tuvq lovg maaig pwrnb sin Eei msia'q txn, fai Ryaaug Jiaj txn Eei sia'q, fai aub leib zruj auq. sai myenb xij zu'g Zivb Revg Eei weig ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
21.17: “Buaj aa-lon, ‘meib Eei txig Jiaj txig Eei zeib fun, haiq taub Eei sin zavg waaig favj Eei, maiq haib taaib fatq fovg hxg ninb Eei Tinb huvb Eei Eang hopq.
21.11: haiq nxm txvj maaib myenb taig, maiq tuvq pia'g uaq nxm txvj. lyemb tia fai maa taig, maiq tuvq pun kanb maaib wij.

23.19: xij zu'g lovg taub yuvb kruq ziag fi'q zwid, Zauj i taub txij Havj Eei pa'ki yuvb kruq txn ziag weig Jiu Tov.
23.38: naaiq se maiq funj pia'g zyruq Eei tivb kov Nxi ziag Eei ka'naaiq, Zauj fovg hxg Eei zivb Eeig, Zauj Jaauq suv lcvd vcvg waag Eei Zauj Zwrtq fim ziag pun zyruq Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq.)
23.31: Zinb maang maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg kov. maiq kunq meib Bua yem haaij, naaiq se txig Jiaj txig yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid.
23.27: “Zyetq Laaj scvb zyepg se fi'q zwid Nxi. xij zu'g kapq zunq zruj leib paaij, zei maiq Eang haiq Euvg, yaag txb lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq fovg hxg pun zyruq.
23.41: mrud Havj Tauj Zyetq Laaj xij zu'g Jiaj zyruq Eei zipq siag Nxi. naaiq se txig Jiaj txig yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid.
23.39: “+‘meib Bua syru paag Zunb kcv, yem Zyetq Laaj zyepg Mmd, xij zu'g Jiaj zyruq Eei zipq pwavq siag Nxi. taaub Nxi se weib hitq Kwrnj Nxi. ta'petq Nxi yaag weib hitq Kwrnj Nxi.
23.10: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘meib Bua Tauj yia xij Jiu pun meib Bua uaq nxm teib puv, syru Byaub Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g txb yetg zeiq taaub Txvj Byaub taaib pun sai myenb.
23.25: maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg Nxib Nxi zruj Eei kov. yaag xij zu'g txb lovg trud puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq fovg hxg pun zyruq. ’+”
23.22: “+‘meib Bua kaatq Byaub, maiq tuvq kaatq Tauj Jomg Deib Len, yaag maiq tuvq Raud Byaub Dxtq. xij zu'g lyrub pun myenb Jomg myenb cvj Zauj meib Bua yem Eei kanb fivj myenb. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.’+”
23.42: meib Bua xij zu'g yem liub siag Nxi. yetg zuvq pwrnb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb xij zu'g yem liub
23.15: “+‘yem tivb kov Nxi Ga'haaq uaq Nxi, tovb txb Byaub zeiq taaib Zunq kiv fovg hxg uaq Nxi, xij zu'g saauq pwavq siag nxm leib paaij.
23.29: yem uaq nxm Nxi, haiq taub maiq zei zyrug Eang ka'naaiq nx, xij zu'g yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg.
23.30: haiq taub yem uaq nxm Nxi zruj haiq Euvg kov, yia zyrug myetg uaq taub. ninb maiq tu'q Zauj ninb Eei myenb yem.

6.18: aa-lon Eei zeib fun, mrud taub mJavg txn, Eang tu'q Eei. naaiq se lovg trud puaq fovg hxg pun zyruq, txig Jiaj txig yetg liud tu'q Eei pwrng. haiq taub mua'q zu'g naaiq teij ka'naaiq zyrug Zivb Revg.’+”
6.3: fai zwrtg tu'q ka'naaiq yaag maiq Eyemg, fai kxvq Jaaq waag Druq zyruj, fai zruj haiq Euvg myenb haib zruj txvg Eei zwid,
6.21: zx'q ka'lanq yrub toj Jyenq Bwrnq, Qruq lovj, an Zcv naatq. cvj mc'q taaib fovg hxg zruj ziag Eei laavb zi'g, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
6.14: “+‘fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g Eei leib Eeig se Navq naaiq. aa-lon Eei txn Bua xij zu'g yem ziab txvb Ra'Myen zx'q fovg hxg Eei laavb zi'g ziag pun zyruq.
6.23: ta'faanb sai myenb fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g, Runb Rung xij zu'g puaq Revg. maiq tuvq Eang.”
6.6: ninb xij zu'g weig ninb zruj txvg Eei zwid txb taub maiq waaig favj Eei pa'ki yuvb kruq Tauj sai myenb uaq pun zyruq. meib kanb xij zu'g funj pa'ki yuvb Eei Jaab zinb Pwij hxpg weig zruj txvg zwid ziag Eei ka'naaiq.
6.2: “sij kxvq maaib myenb paamd zwid, maiq zyepg zua'q Eei zruj pun zyruq,   se ninb Duaq Jwavg laavd Eei kxb yrud yem myenb Eei tivb zinb, fai myenb Jwij pun ninb syru Eei ka'naaiq, fai ninb nimg myenb Eei ka'naaiq, fai zruj pun myenb zu'g Kwei,
6.20: “naaiq se lovg yrub xn aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua zruj sai myenb uaq Nxi xij zu'g fovg hxg pun zyruq. xij zu'g txb i mx'q Bwrnb mwrng weib Nxib Nxi ziag Eei laavb zi'g. luvb Dxm fovg hxg yetg pwrng, luvb Mwavj yetg pwrng.
6.28: zruq naaiq teij xq Eei niab mx xij zu'g Bx'q huq. mq paag sij kxvq lovg tovb si'q Zcv zruq nx, xij zu'g Raatq, cvj lovg uam Raauj.
6.7: sai myenb zyrug yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Tevj ninb fi'q zwid. Navq naaig, maiq kunq ninb zruj haiq Euvg txvg zwid, ninb tu'q kwavg mig a'q.”
6.29: ta'faanb sai myenb Eei Mwavq txig, mJavg txn uaq teij, Eang tu'q Eei. se Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq.
6.17: maiq tuvq an pivq zi'q. naaiq se lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun yia Eei ka'naaiq, tovb yia Jiu pun sai myenb penj ninb Bua Eei pwrng. se Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei, Navq ziag fi'q zwid Zauj zruj txvg zwid ziag Eei ka'naaiq Zivb Revg.
6.30: mq paag sij kxvq sai myenb txb haiq taub ziag fi'q zwid Eei scvb Kuq Ryaamq pia'g wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub, yem Zivb Revg uaq Qovj fi'q zwid, maiq tuvq Eang uaq taub scvb Kuq Eei xq. xij zu'g puaq Revg.
6.27: ta'faanb haiq Euvg mua'q zu'g naaiq teij xq, uaq Euvg zyrug Zivb Revg mig a'q. sij kxvq uaq taub scvb Kuq Eei Ryaamq kua'q zu'g lwi, xij zu'g yem nxm Zivb Revg Eei txvj Roj Revg.
6.11: Ga'haaq xij zu'g yeng Gxi lwib hruj cvj zu'q kanb teij, zyrug txb saaiq Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq Tauj nxm maiq maaib wij Eei txvj.
6.5: fai ninb weig haiq Euvg ka'naaiq Druq zyruj Jaaq Eei. txb ka'naaiq mivb ziag weig zruj txvg zwid uaq Nxi, ninb xij zu'g Twij Revg cvj pwib pyaa kruq Eei yetg kruq pun uaq teij ka'naaiq Eei zyruq.
6.9: “xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx Paaiq aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua, ‘puaq ziag Eei leib Eeig se Navq naaiq. puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq xij zu'g yem ziab txvb kub vwaaig zyavb mwrnd puaq Tauj luvb Fav. ziab txvb Eei trud yaag xij zu'g zanb zang zia'g Jyenq.
6.16: zevg Fiag Eei pwrng, aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua Eang. maiq tuvq an pivq. yaag xij zu'g yem nxm Zivb Revg Eei txvj, se yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei laatg ka'Euad mcvj Eang.
6.4: uaq taub zyrug zruj txvg, maaib zwid a'q. ninb xij zu'g Twij Rwrnj ninb nimg Eei, fai pun myenb zu'g Kwei Eei, fai myenb Jwij pun ninb Eei ka'naaiq, fai zwrtg taaib Eei ka'naaiq,
6.10: sai myenb xij zu'g zu'q la'maab Dia Eei lwib Daauq Zauj la'maab Dia Eei hruj, zx'q yem ziab txvb puaq liud ziag Eei ka'naaiq Eei saaiq, an Jyenq ziab txvb ka'Len.
6.22: lovg yrub xn aa-lon Eei haiq taub zeib fun Ripg Jyenq zruj sai myenb, xij zu'g zx'q naaiq teij fovg hxg Eei laavb zi'g yetg zuvq puaq Revg ziag pun zyruq. naaiq se yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid.
6.12: yem ziab txvb Eei trud xij zu'g zanb zang zia'g Jyenq, maiq tuvq pun taig. sai myenb Dxmb Dxm xij zu'g Jaa zaavb cvj zx'q puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq zweib yetq zweib Eeig Eei an trud kub vwaaig. cvj zx'q ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei scvb Kuq Mei Jaa kub vwaaig.
6.15: sai myenb xij zu'g zx'q yetg Eau Bwrnb mwrng zxpg Jyenq ka'lanq yrub, Zauj Yetq Jyenq laavb zi'g Eei yetg zuvq huv, an ziab txvb kub vwaaig puaq ziag weig pun zyruq Javj fovg hxg Eei myenb, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
6.13: ziab txvb Eei trud xij zu'g zanb zang zia'g Jyenq. Zinb maang maiq tuvq pun taig.
6.26: pun Tevj ziag fi'q zwid uaq taub sai myenb Eang naaiq taub scvb Kuq. yaag xij zu'g yem Zivb Revg Eei txvj, se yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei laatg ka'Euad mcvj Eang.
6.25: “xij zu'g Buaj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua, ‘ziag fi'q zwid Eei leib Eeig se Navq naaiq. ziag fi'q zwid Eei scvb Kuq xij zu'g yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen taij, se yem taij puaq ziag Eei scvb Kuq Eei txvj taij. naaiq se kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq.

2.3: fovg hxg liud, zevg Fiag Eei laavb zi'g penj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Eei pwrng mig a'q. naaiq se yetg pwrng kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq, yem lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei ka'naaiq zx'q Zwrtq taaib.
2.8: lovg naaiq pua'q ka'naaiq zruj fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g, xij zu'g txb taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq. xij zu'g Jiu pun sai myenb, sai myenb zyrug txb Tauj ziab txvb.
2.9: sai myenb xij zu'g zx'q teij fovg hxg Eei laavb zi'g Zwrtq zruj Javj Eei pwrng, an ziab txvb puaq weig zruj lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
2.7: sij kxvq ziag Eei laavb zi'g yem Zcv zin taaib, xij zu'g lovg Bwrnb mwrng Qruq Jyenq ka'lanq yrub.
2.5: sij kxvq fovg hxg Eei laavb zi'g se yem Zcv naatq taaib, xij zu'g lovg Bwrnb mwrng zxpg Jyenq ka'lanq yrub, yaag maiq tuvq an pivq.
2.16: sai myenb xij zu'g zx'q Zwrtq teij Byaub Bwrnq Zauj yrub Zauj yetg zuvq huv zruj Javj Eei pwrng, lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq.
2.14: “+‘sij kxvq txb taaub Txvj laavb zi'g taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq, xij zu'g Kavj Gaai mxg mwrng.
2.4: “+‘sij kxvq fovg hxg Eei laavb zi'g se yem zi'q Fuaq Eei Roj zi'q txb taaib, xij zu'g lovg Bwrnb mwrng. se lovg maiq an pivq, zxpg Jyenq ka'lanq yrub Eei Fuaq, fai maiq an pivq, Raatq Jyenq ka'lanq yrub Eei Fuab pia'g.
2.2: txb Tauj aa-lon Eei txn, sai myenb Bua uaq. sai myenb zyrug zx'q yetg Eau naaiq teij Bwrnb mwrng Zauj yrub Zauj yetg zuvq huv zruj Javj Eei pwrng an Jyenq ziab txvb kub vwaaig puaq ziag. naaiq se lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
2.6: xij zu'g zx'q Fuaq mc'q mwrng, zx'q ka'lanq yrub toj Jyenq. naaiq se fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g.
2.13: meib Bua fovg hxg ziag Eei yetg zuvq laavb zi'g xij zu'g Yetq Jyenq Rauq. maiq tuvq pun Rauq tavj, weig zu'g Rauq piuj mevb Tinb huvb Zauj meib Bua lyepg Eei vcvg waag. meib Bua fovg hxg Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq xij zu'g Yetq Rauq.
2.12: txb naaiq teij i Euvg taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq weig zruj taaub Txvj Zunb kcv tu'q Eei. mq paag maiq tuvq an ziab txvb puaq weib Daav Eei Qiaj.
2.15: yaag xij zu'g Yetq ka'lanq yrub Zauj huv. naaiq se ziag fovg hxg Eei laavb zi'g.
2.11: “+‘ta'faanb fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq Eei laavb zi'g, maiq tuvq an pivq. meib Bua lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei haiq Euvg, Zinb maang maiq tuvq zxpg pivq fai mweib txvb.
2.1: “+‘haiq taub txb laavb zi'g taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq, xij zu'g txb Bwrnb mwrng. xij zu'g toj ka'lanq yrub Yetq Jyenq, zx'q teij huv an Jyenq,
2.10: fovg hxg liud, zevg Fiag Eei laavb zi'g penj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua Eei mig a'q. naaiq se Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq, yem lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei ka'naaiq zevg Fiag Eei pwrng.

20.18: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub mJavg txn pweij msia'q txn txij maaib sinb yeng Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g pun ninb Bua i taub yem kanb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg, weig zu'g ninb Bua txvg Zivb Revg Eei leid pun kanb maaib wij.
20.8: xij zu'g kan lovj yia Eei livg, ei Jyenq zruj Revg. yia se zyruq, tovb pun meib Bua Zivb Revg uaq taub.
20.3: yia kanb yaag xij Byenq Myen pun uaq taub yaag pun ninb yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg, weig zu'g ninb zx'q taub ninb Eei fu'Jweiq fuvj pun mo-lekq zyenb, zyrug zruj pun yia Eei sivj ting maaib wij yaag paaig yia Eei Zivb Revg Buaj.
20.21: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub mJavg txn lovg muab txig Eei auq, naaiq se zruj maiq Zivb Revg Eei sig, paaig zu'g ninb Eei muab txig. ninb Bua zyrug maiq haib maaib fu'Jweiq.
20.14: “+‘sij kxvq myenb lovg i sia'g maag zruj auq se waaig haig Eei sig. zuvq xij zu'g zx'q ninb Bua pua taub lovg trud puaq taig weig maiq pun waaig sig yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj.
20.23: yaag maiq tuvq kan yem uaq nxm teib puv Eei myenb Eei leid, tovb yia xij zung Zwrtq meib Bua uaq Daavg mcvj Eei fivb fivj myenb Eei leid. laaij ninb Bua zruj naaiq teij yetg zuvq sig yia yruj! haig ninb Bua.
20.6: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub mivb lxd myenb Tevj kaanq hei fai Bruq kwaaj, se Navq maaib Yiab Hruq Eei myenb nx. yia xij Byenq Myen pun uaq taub, yaag pun ninb yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg.
20.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘ta'faanb i-saa-laa-en myenb, fai yem i-saa-laa-en teib puv Eei kanb fivj myenb, haiq taub zx'q kanb Eei fu'Jweiq fuvj pun mo-lekq zyenb, zuvq xij zu'g zx'q uaq taub taij taig. zwavj pc'g fivj xij zu'g zx'q la'pyeiq zov taig ninb.
20.20: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub mJavg txn pweij Juab maag fai Riab maag fai tomb myavb maag fai myavb maag zyrug paaig zu'g ninb Eei pc'g tiaj fai yrub tiaj fai tomb naub tiaj fai naub tiaj. ninb Bua i taub xij zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid. Tauj taig ninb Bua yaag maiq haib maaib fu'Jweiq.
20.24: mq paag yia Buaj Jiaj meib Bua, “yia xij zx'q naaiq nxm teib puv Jiu pun meib Bua, zruj penj meib Bua Ripg Eei teib puv, se Daub Truq lovj Eei teib puv.” yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, se yem maang fivj kinq meib Bua Zwrtq taaib uaq taub.
20.7: “+‘xij zu'g saaj kanb Zivb Revg taaib, weig zu'g yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
20.19: “+‘maiq tuvq pweij meib Eei krub maag fai muab maag fai txg teib fai Riab maag. Navq naaiq zruj se paaig zu'g Jwavg Ryaamb fei Eei Zyenb Ze'q. ninb Bua i taub zuvq xij zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid.
20.17: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub lovg kanb Eei txg fai muag, maiq kunq se tia Eei sia'q fai maa Eei sia'q, txv Jaa, Jwavg txvj pweij, se Eaiq haig Eei sig. ninb Bua xij zu'g txv Jyenq ninb Bua Eei myenb zu'g Pai kwavg. uaq taub mJavg txn paaig kanb Eei txg fai muag zyrug xij zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid.
20.27: “+‘maiq kunq mJavg msia'q, meib Bua haiq taub Tevj myenb kaanq hei fai Bruq kwaaj, zuvq xij zu'g pun ninb Bua zu'g taig. xij zu'g lovg la'pyeiq zov taig. ninb Bua kanb Eei zwid ninb Bua kanb xij zu'g Daamb txv.’+”
20.11: “+‘sij kxvq myenb pweij kanb Eei tia Eei auq zyrug paaig ninb Eei tia. zuvq xij zu'g zx'q ninb Bua i taub taij taig. ninb Bua kanb xij zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid.
20.5: yia kanb xij Byenq Myen pun uaq taub Zauj ninb Eei Mwavq txig yaag pun ninb yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg, lyemb Zauj ninb maaib Yiab Hruq kan mo-lekq zyenb uaq teij.
20.9: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub zyruj ninb Eei tia fai maa, xij zu'g zx'q uaq taub taij taig. ninb zyruj tia fai maa, ninb kanb xij zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid.
20.16: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub msia'q txn txb kanb pun scvb Kuq scv, xij zu'g lyemb msia'q txn, lyemb scvb Kuq taij taig. i taub zuvq xij zu'g taij kwavg. ninb Bua kanb xij zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid.
20.4: uaq taub myenb zx'q taub ninb Eei fu'Jweiq fuvj pun mo-lekq zyenb uaq zang, sij kxvq pwrnb teig pc'g fivj Navq Fipq Jyenq mziv maiq pwatg nx, yaag maiq zov taig ninb,
20.10: “+‘sij kxvq myenb Yenj kanb taub myenb Eei auq, zuvq xij zu'g pun ninb Bua i taub zu'g taig.
20.22: “+‘xij zu'g kan lovj yia Eei yetg zuvq livg Zauj tiub tiub leid, yaag ei Jyenq zruj, weig pun tovb yia ib zang txb meib Bua mivb yem uaq nxm teib puv maiq loq meib Bua Zwrtq.
20.12: “+‘sij kxvq myenb pweij kanb Eei Bwavd, zuvq xij zu'g zx'q ninb Bua i taub taij taig. ninb Bua zruj maiq lwrnj hxvg Eei sig. ninb Bua kanb xij zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid.
20.15: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub mJavg txn Yenj scvb Kuq, xij zu'g zx'q ninb taij taig. yaag xij zu'g zx'q uaq taub scvb Kuq taij.
20.13: “+‘sij kxvq mJavg txn pweij mJavg txn txvj msia'q txn, ninb Bua zruj Eei se kamb Riaq Eei sig. zuvq xij zu'g zx'q ninb Bua i taub taij taig. ninb Bua kanb xij zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid.
20.26: meib Bua xij zu'g weig yia Zivb Revg, weig zu'g yia, zyruq, se Zivb Revg Eei, yaag yem maang fivj kinq meib Bua Zwrtq taaib penj yia Eei pc'g fivj.
20.25: “+‘weig naaiq meib Bua xij zu'g zx'q maaib wij Zauj maiq maaib wij Eei scvb Kuq pun Gxi, maaib wij Zauj maiq maaib wij Eei nx'g. yaag maiq tuvq laaij yia kinq Zwrtq maaib wij Eei scvb Kuq fai nx'g fai Exv Dau Eei ka'naaiq pun kanb maaib wij.

24.18: haiq taub Bx'q taig myenb Eei scvb Kuq, uaq taub xij zu'g cvj pwib scvb Kuq. se mcvg pwib mcvg.
24.8: mrud nxm tivb kov Nxi, aa-lon xij zu'g weig i-saa-laa-en myenb txb naaiq teij Fuaq mivb yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen liug leid, se zruj yetg liud Eei vcvg waag.
24.3: aa-lon xij zu'g yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub ka'Euad, lcvd vcvg waag faav uaq Qovj Eei Bc'g kcvb Dia ka'Eiag, liug leid tav pun naaiq teij tav yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen zyavb mwrnd zia'g Jyenq Tauj luvb Dxm. naaiq se txig Jiaj txig yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid.
24.21: haiq taub Bx'q taig scvb Kuq, xij zu'g pwib scvb Kuq. mq paag haiq taub taij myenb taig, uaq taub kanb xij zu'g tivg zwid taij taig.
24.14: “txb Ki zyruq Eei Buaj uaq taub myenb Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq. mwavj haid ninb Ki Eei waag uaq teij myenb xij zu'g txb puad maan Jyenq ninb Eei mGxvq. zwavj myenb zyrug xij zu'g lovg la'pyeiq zov taig ninb.
24.23: mo-se Navq naaiq nx Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ninb Bua zyrug txb Ki zyruq uaq taub myenb Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq lovg la'pyeiq zov taig ninb. Navq naaig, i-saa-laa-en myenb ei Jyenq zyruq Buaj mo-se Eei waag zruj.
24.6: zx'q taaib an Jyenq yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen uaq nxm Jyemb tiab kub vwaaig, Baib Jyenq zruj i lyrud, yetg lyrud Ju'q nxm.
24.2: “xij zu'g Paaiq i-saa-laa-en myenb txb zaaj taaib kaub lovj Jiaj Eei ka'lanq yrub weig puaq tav, pun tav zanb zang zia'g Jyenq.
24.20: Buvq Jaauq Buvq, mziv Jaauq mziv, Eaab Jaauq Eaab. Navq haiq nx zruj pun myenb mun yaag xij zu'g Navq uaq nx zruj pun ninb.
24.7: cvj zx'q Zivb Revg huv an Jyenq naaiq teij i lyrud Fuaq weig pun zyruq Javj. naaiq teij huv tiq Fuaq lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq.
24.19: haiq taub zruj pun myenb mun, ninb Navq haiq nx zruj yaag xij zu'g Navq uaq nx zruj Jaauq ninb.
24.17: “+‘haiq taub taij myenb, uaq taub xij zu'g tivg zwid taij taig.
24.11: naaiq taub i-saa-laa-en msia'q txn Eei txn lovg zyruj Eei waag Ki zyruq Eei Buaj. myenb zyrug txb ninb mivb Tauj mo-se uaq. (naaiq taub myenb Eei maa Eei Buaj heug se-lo-mitq, se Daan fivj, Dipg-li Eei sia'q.)
24.5: “xij zu'g lovg Bwrnb mwrng zruj zyepg Eeig nxm Fuaq, yetg nxm lovg pyei mx'q pyenj Bwrnq, cvj zi'q taaib.
24.9: naaiq teij Fuaq penj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua yetg liud tu'q Eei pwrng. ninb Bua xij zu'g yem Zivb Revg Eei txvj Eang weig zu'g se lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq.”
24.16: haiq taub Ki zyruq Eei Buaj, zuvq xij zu'g taij taig. zwavj myenb xij zu'g zx'q la'pyeiq zov taig ninb. maiq kunq kanb fivj myenb fai pwrnb fivj myenb, haiq taub Ki zyruq Eei Buaj, zuvq xij zu'g taij taig.
24.4: ninb xij zu'g zanb zang liug leid yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen uaq nxm Jyemb tavb Jaaj Eei tav.
24.10: maaib taub myenb, ninb Eei maa i-saa-laa-en myenb, ninb Eei tia i-yipq myenb. maaib Nxi nx, naaiq taub myenb Zauj taub i-saa-laa-en myenb yem uaq Zyavq Rcv Jaaj.
24.22: maiq kunq kanb fivj myenb fai Jwavg fivj myenb, xij zu'g Jwavg naaiq tiub leid lovg. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.’+”
24.12: ninb Bua zyrug zx'q naaiq taub myenb Kwrnj Jyenq Tauj hiuq tu'q zyruq xij ninb Bua Navq haiq nx zruj.
24.15: xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘sij kxvq haiq taub zyruj ninb Eei Tinb huvb, ninb kanb xij zu'g Daamb txv.

7.18: sij kxvq ta'faam Nxi Eang naaiq teij ziag Eei xq nx, zyruq zyrug maiq zipq ninb fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. se maiq hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq. zuvq funj naaiq teij ka'naaiq maaib wij. haiq taub Eang zyrug zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid a'q.
7.8: haiq taub sai myenb Tevj haiq taub puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei scvb Kuq, uaq taub sai myenb zyrug tu'q scvb Kuq Eei Dopq.
7.33: aa-lon Eei txn, tovb zx'q ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei scvb Kuq Ryaamq Zauj Mei fovg hxg uaq taub, xij zu'g tu'q Byaaug puv zaub zwib weig zruj ninb Eei pwrng.
7.3: yetg zuvq Mei xij zu'g fovg hxg, se zx'q Jung Eei tweiq Zauj yetg zuvq yem Hruq Eei Mei, lyemb Zc'g Jaavb Mei,
7.32: yem meib Bua ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq, xij zu'g zx'q Byaaug puv zaub zwib fuvj pun sai myenb.
7.21: sij kxvq haiq taub mua'q zu'g maaib wij Eei ka'naaiq, maiq kunq se myenb Eei wij fai scvb Kuq Eei, fai haiq Euvg kamb Riaq Eei, maaib wij Eei ka'naaiq, cvj Eang fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq weig Jiu Tov Eei xq nx, uaq taub xij zu'g yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg.’+”
7.35: naaiq se zx'q aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua fuvj zruj sai myenb fub suj zyruq uaq Nxi tivg pun ninb Bua Eei pwrng. se yem i-saa-laa-en myenb lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei ka'naaiq zx'q Zwrtq Eei pwrng.
7.14: naaiq teij Fuaq xij zu'g txb yetg Euvg yetg nxm zruj ziag Eei ka'naaiq fovg hxg pun zyruq. naaiq se penj sai myenb Eei pwrng, tovb zx'q ziag weig Jiu Tov uaq taub scvb Kuq Eei Ryaamq Pyetq ziab txvb uaq taub sai myenb.
7.23: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb, ‘meib Bua maiq tuvq Eang vovb Mei, pa'ki yuvb fai yuvb Eei Mei.
7.6: ta'faanb sai myenb Eei Mwavq txig, mJavg txn uaq teij, Eang naaiq teij xq tu'q Eei, mq paag xij zu'g yem Zivb Revg Eei txvj Eang weig zu'g naaiq se kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq.
7.34: yem i-saa-laa-en myenb ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq, yia zx'q Zunq kiv Eei lx'g Ywav xq Zauj fovg hxg pun Eei zwib pun aa-lon sai myenb Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua weig zruj ninb Bua yetg liud xij zu'g tu'q Eei pwrng.’+”
7.2: ziag fi'q zruj txvg zwid Eei scvb Kuq xij zu'g yem taij puaq ziag Eei scvb Kuq Eei txvj taij. zx'q Ryaamq Pyetq Wiv kxmj ziab txvb.
7.36: tovb lovg yrub xn aa-lon Bua zruj sai myenb uaq Nxi, zyruq Paaiq i-saa-laa-en myenb zx'q naaiq teij Jiu pun ninb Bua weig zruj ninb Bua txig Jiaj txig yetg liud xij zu'g tu'q Eei pwrng.
7.20: mq paag haiq taub maaib wij cvj Eang fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq weig Jiu Tov Eei xq nx, uaq taub xij zu'g yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg.
7.24: scvb Kuq kanb taig fai zu'g Yiab ka'naaiq vaatg taig, ninb Eei Mei lovg zruj kanb Euvg tu'q Eei, mq paag Zinb maang maiq tuvq Eang.
7.7: “+‘ziag fi'q zwid Zauj ziag fi'q zruj txvg zwid se fib Navq Eei. maaib Du'g Euvg leid Navq. Tevj fi'q zwid uaq taub sai myenb tu'q naaiq teij ziag Eei ka'naaiq a'q.
7.29: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘haiq taub fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq, xij zu'g yem ninb fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq zx'q Zwrtq teij levg Jeiq fovg hxg pun zyruq.
7.19: “+‘sij kxvq naaiq teij xq zu'g haiq Euvg maaib wij Eei ka'naaiq, maiq tuvq Eang. xij zu'g puaq trud Revg. haiq taub maiq maaib wij, Eang naaiq teij xq tu'q Eei.
7.17: Tauj ta'faam Nxi Zxg maaib zevg Eei nx, xij zu'g puaq kwavg.
7.38: se zyruq yem si-naai Bov Paaiq mo-se, tovb mo-se yem si-naai teib puvb Waav Paaiq i-saa-laa-en myenb txb ka'naaiq taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq uaq Nxi.
7.31: sai myenb zyrug zx'q Mei an ziab txvb kub vwaaig puaq, mq paag lx'g Ywav xq penj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua Eei pwrng mig a'q.
7.30: lovg trud ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei ka'naaiq, fovg hxg Eei myenb kanb xij zu'g txb taaib. xij zu'g txb scvb Kuq Eei Mei Zauj lx'g Ywav xq. lx'g Ywav xq xij zu'g yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Zunq kiv weig zruj Zunq kiv fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq.
7.27: haiq taub Eang haiq Euvg Ryaamq, uaq taub xij zu'g yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg.’+”
7.11: “+‘naaiq se myenb txb ka'naaiq fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq weig Jiu Tov Eei leib Eeig.
7.5: sai myenb zyrug an ziab txvb, lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq. se weig fi'q zruj txvg zwid Eei ka'naaiq.
7.9: haiq Euvg fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g, maiq kunq yem zi'q Fuaq Eei Roj zi'q, fai yem Zcv zin, fai yem Zcv naatq, yetg zuvq penj Tevj fovg hxg uaq taub sai myenb Eei mig a'q.
7.16: “+‘sij kxvq fovg hxg ziag weig Jaauq suv lcvd Eei vcvg waag fai Zwrtq fim ziag, ziag Eei xq xij zu'g uaq Nxi Eang. zevg Fiag Eei Tauj ta'Eeig Nxi Eang tu'q Eei.
7.37: naaiq teij yetg zuvq se fovg hxg ziag Eei leib Eeig. maaib puaq ziag Eei, ziag Eei laavb zi'g, ziag fi'q zwid, ziag fi'q zruj txvg zwid Eei, ziag weig xn zruj sai myenb, Zauj ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei leib Eeig.
7.4: Zauj i nxm Eutg zeiq, Zauj peu Eutg zeiq nitq Jaaiq Eei panq yrub. pwav Jyenq Lan Eei xb Byxvd yaag xij zu'g Zauj Eutg zeiq zx'q Zwrtq.
7.10: fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g yetg zuvq, maiq kunq zxpg Jyenq yrub fai maiq zxpg, se aa-lon Eei txn Bua pun Gxi lovg.
7.12: “+‘sij kxvq myenb txb ka'naaiq taaib fovg hxg weig lcvd zivb zyruq nx, xij zu'g lovg maiq an pivq, zxpg Jyenq ka'lanq yrub Eei Fuaq, maiq an pivq Eei Fuab pia'g Raatq Jyenq ka'lanq yrub, Zauj Bwrnb mwrng zxpg Jyenq ka'lanq yrub zruj taaib Eei Fuaq Zauj Jyenq ziag weig lcvd zivb Eei scvb Kuq.
7.15: ziag weig Jiu Tov lcvd zivb Eei xq xij zu'g yem ziag uaq Nxi Eang Tauj Revg. maiq tuvq lyrub Tauj ta'Eeig Dxm.
7.13: txb fovg hxg ziag weig Jiu Tov lcvd zivb zyruq Eei ka'naaiq Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g txb an pivq Eei Fuaq Zauj Jyenq.
7.1: “+‘fi'q zruj txvg zwid Eei leib Eeig se Navq naaiq. se kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq.
7.26: maiq kunq meib Bua yem haaij, maiq tuvq Eang haiq Euvg nx'g fai haiq Euvg scvb Kuq Eei Ryaamq.
7.25: haiq taub Eang lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg  pun zyruq Eei scvb Kuq Mei, uaq taub xij zu'g yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg.

19.18: “+‘maiq tuvq Jaauq syrub fai nipg win kanb Eei kxb yrud, zuvq xij zu'g Namq myenb Navq Namq kanb nx. yia se zyruq.
19.8: haiq taub Eang naaiq teij ziag Eei ka'naaiq zuvq xij zu'g Daam ninb kanb Eei zwid, weig zu'g ninb zruj pun zyruq Eei Zivb Revg ka'naaiq maaib wij. uaq taub yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj xij zu'g Pai kwavg.
19.33: “+‘sij kxvq maaib kanb fivj myenb Zauj meib Bua yem meib Bua Eei teib puv, maiq tuvq zruj to'g ninb.
19.3: “+‘meib Bua kx'g myenb xij zu'g Tovj nimg kanb Eei tiaj maag. yaag xij zu'g kan lovj yia Eei nxmb nxm tivb kov Nxi. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
19.32: “+‘yem myenb koj myenb Eei Ra'Myen xij zu'g sruq Jiad sin. xij zu'g Taaib Havb Jeiq Lav Eei myenb, yaag xij zu'g kamb Riaj meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb. yia se zyruq.
19.21: mq paag uaq taub mJavg txn xij zu'g txb taub pa'ki yuvb kruq Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg weig zruj txvg Eei zwid ziag pun zyruq.
19.35: “+‘meib Bua Dx'g fai Ryav fai Laau haiq Euvg, maiq tuvq Kwei haiq taub.
19.14: “+‘maiq tuvq zyruj mnxmb Duv Eei myenb. yaag maiq tuvq zx'q ka'naaiq an Jauq pun mziv mcvb Eei myenb Di'q zu'g Dxpg. xij zu'g kamb Riaj, Taaib meib Eei Tinb huvb. yia se zyruq.
19.23: “+‘meib Bua pia'g Kaa-naa-an teib puv zwavj haiq Euvg pyruq, xij zu'g keg pua Havj, maiq tuvq Eang.
19.6: ziag Eei ka'naaiq xij zu'g yem ziag uaq Nxi Eang, fai ta'Eeig Nxi. Tauj ta'faam Nxi maaib zevg Eei nx, xij zu'g puaq kwavg.
19.34: xij zu'g funj yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj Eei kanb fivj myenb Zauj pwrnb teig myenb fib Navq, yaag xij zu'g Namq ninb Navq Namq kanb nx, weig zu'g zinb Daavg meib Bua yem i-yipq teib puv zruj kanb fivj myenb. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
19.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb, ‘meib Bua xij zu'g Zivb Revg weig zu'g yia, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, se Zivb Revg.
19.36: Ryavj xij zu'g hxpg, Ryavb txb xij zu'g hxpg, Laau Eei ka'naaiq yaag xij zu'g hxpg. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, tovb txb meib Bua yem i-yipq teib puv Zwrtq taaib uaq taub.
19.20: “+‘sij kxvq maaib taub mJavg txn pweij taub nrub peid, uaq taub nrub peid yaag maaib myenb kxvq zyavb ninb mig a'q, mq paag maiq kcvb tu'q zua'g, maiq kcvb tu'q puvj Gxi, xij zu'g zaab mavg ninb Bua Eei sig. yaag maiq tuvq taij ninb Bua, weig zu'g uaq taub nrub peid maiq kcvb tu'q puvj Gxi.
19.24: ta'feij Havj zyavb Eei pyruq yetg zuvq se Zivb Revg Eei, xij zu'g fovg hxg weig Zev zyruq.
19.28: myenb taig yaag maiq tuvq weig ninb Bua kaatq kanb Eei sin fai Ryepq pyavb. yia se zyruq.
19.7: Tauj ta'faam Nxi Zxg cvj Eang, naaiq teij ka'naaiq maaib wij a'q. zyruq yaag maiq zipq naaiq teij fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq.
19.29: “+‘maiq tuvq paaig meib Bua Eei sia'q, aapq zruj maaig pwrnb sin Eei myenb. Riaj zyavb nxm teib puv Eei myenb haib penj maaig pwrnb sin Eei Jauq. teib puv zyrug maaib waaig sig pwavq Revg.
19.19: “+‘meib Bua xij zu'g ei Revg yia Eei livg. “+‘maiq tuvq pun meib Eei yetg Euvg scvb Kuq zxpg ta'Eeig Euvg Eei pwrnq. “+‘maiq tuvq lovg i Euvg Eim Jwavg Rov Deig zwavj. “+‘maiq tuvq zu'q lovg i Euvg swij zxpg Jyenq zruj taaib Eei lwib hruj.
19.17: “+‘maiq tuvq yem Hruq Rxv meib Eei kxb yrud. zuvq xij zu'g mivb Kwinj ninb weig pun kanb maiq zu'g Zauj ninb Daam zwid.
19.31: “+‘maiq tuvq mivb lxd myenb Tevj kaanq hei fai Bruq kwaaj. Navq naaiq zruj meib Bua zyrug laaij ninb Bua maaib wij. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
19.30: “+‘xij zu'g kan lovj yia Eei nxmb nxm tivb kov Nxi. yaag xij zu'g Taaib yia Eei sivj ting. yia se zyruq.
19.27: “+‘maiq tuvq Japq meib Bua Eei Ba'pyei pcvb Eei Wiv kxmj mGxvq.
19.11: “+‘maiq tuvq zruj za'g. “+‘maiq tuvq kxvb pc'g. “+‘maiq tuvq laanb Duaq laanb.
19.5: “+‘meib Bua fovg hxg ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq pun zyruq Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g zruj hxpg weig pun zyruq a'Neiq zipq.
19.9: “+‘meib Bua kaatq Byaub, maiq tuvq kaatq Tauj Jomg Deib Len, yaag maiq tuvq Raud Byaub Dxtq.
19.16: “+‘maiq tuvq yem meib Eei myenb Bu'Dovj Jiaj naaiq Jiaj uaq kxvq waab huq. “+‘yaag maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg hxig myenb Eei mcvg. yia se zyruq.
19.37: “+‘xij zu'g kan lovj yia Eei yetg zuvq livg Zauj tiub tiub leid. xij zu'g ei Jyenq zruj Revg. yia se zyruq. ’+”
19.4: “+‘maiq tuvq kwavg yia cvj zavg miub favj. yaag maiq tuvq toj miub favj taaib weig kanb paaij. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
19.10: maiq tuvq kc'q Revg yem a'vung Wivj Eei pyruq. yaag maiq tuvq Raud a'vung pyrub Dxtq. xij zu'g lyrub pun myenb Jomg myenb cvj Zauj meib Bua yem Eei kanb fivj myenb. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
19.22: sai myenb zyrug lovg uaq taub pa'ki yuvb kruq yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen ziag Tevj ninb fi'q ninb zruj txvg Eei zwid. ninb Eei zwid zyrug tu'q kwavg liud a'q.
19.12: “+‘maiq tuvq zyavq Jyenq yia Eei Buaj lcvd waag mq paag Jaaq Eei, zyrug paaig zu'g meib Eei Tinb huvb Eei Buaj. yia se zyruq.
19.15: “+‘xij zu'g pcvb fim Eei syemq zwid Beng sig. yaag maiq tuvq Kuvj prug myenb Jomg myenb fai Kuvj Tevj myenb maaib myenb. xij zu'g pcvb fim Eei syemq myenb.
19.13: “+‘maiq tuvq Kwei myenb fai Zaavq myenb Eei ka'naaiq. “+‘maiq tuvq lyrub Zivq taaib zruj kov Eei myenb Eei kovb zinb Jiaj mwrnd.
19.26: “+‘maiq tuvq Eang Zxg maaib Ryaamq yem Jyenq Eei xq. “+‘maiq tuvq Bruq kwaaj fai zruj haiq Euvg myenq.
19.25: mq paag ta'Mmd Havj meib Bua Eang naaiq teij Dyavj Eei pyruq tu'q a'q. Navq naaiq zruj, Dyavj zyrug zyavb pyruq Zamq Jyenq faauj. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.

17.3: haiq taub i-saa-laa-en myenb taij vovb, pa'ki yuvb txn fai yuvb, maiq kunq yem Dopg liub Zyavq ka'Euad taij fai yem ka'Eiag,
17.8: “xij zu'g Buaj ninb Bua, ‘haiq taub i-saa-laa-en myenb fai yem ninb Bua ka'Euad Eei kanb fivj myenb fovg hxg ka'naaiq weig puaq ziag fai ziag weig haiq Euvg,

5.16: uaq taub yaag xij zu'g Jaauq suv tovb ninb Qyemj Jyenq, maiq kcvb Zwrtq Eei pwrng Zivb Revg ka'naaiq, cvj pwib pyaa kruq Eei yetg kruq pun sai myenb. sai myenb zyrug lovg yuvb kruq Tevj ninb fi'q zwid. ninb Eei zwid zyrug tu'q kwavg mig a'q.
5.17: “sij kxvq myenb paamd zwid, zruj tovb zyruq hatg maiq tuvq zruj Eei haiq tiub leid, maiq kunq ninb maiq hiuq tu'q ninb zruj Eei, ninb txvg mig a'q. xij zu'g Daam zwid a'q.
5.4: “+‘fai sij kxvq myenb Javj maiq zaaig zyrug hruq xij zruj yetg Euvg, maiq kunq lovj fai Zyruq, se la'kwaib hruq Tauj haiq Euvg yaag maiq kx'g Jaav, ninb yetq hiuq tu'q ninb zruj Eei, ninb zyrug maaib zwid mig a'q.
5.2: “+‘fai sij kxvq maaib myenb Za'g prug mua'q zu'g maaib wij Eei ka'naaiq Navq Yiab zxib Eei sei, scvb Kuq Eei sei, fai Exv Dau maaib wij Eei ka'naaib taig, yaag maiq kx'g Jaav, ninb maaib wij zyrug maaib zwid a'q.
5.6: laaij ninb zruj txvg zu'g tivg Eei zwid, xij zu'g txb taub yem yuvb kwanb taaib Eei yuvb zeig fai pa'ki yuvb zeig Tauj zyruq Eei Ra'Myen zruj ziag fi'q zwid Eei ka'naaiq. sai myenb zyrug weig ninb paamd Eei zwid Tevj ninb fi'q suv Revg.
5.13: Navq naaiq zruj liud, sai myenb weig naaiq taub myenb fi'q tovb ninb zruj txvg naaiq teij Eei haiq Euvg zwid. ninb Eei zwid zyrug tu'q kwavg mig a'q. zevg Fiag Eei Bwrnb mwrng penj sai myenb Eei, Navq fovg hxg Eei laavb zi'g uaq nx.’+”
5.12: xij zu'g txb naaiq teij Bwrnb mwrng taaib Jiu pun sai myenb. sai myenb zyrug zx'q yetg Eau Bwrnb mwrng weig pun zyruq Javj fovg hxg Eei myenb. sai myenb zyrug an Jyenq ziab txvb, lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei ka'naaiq kub vwaaig puaq. naaiq se ziag fi'q zwid Eei ka'naaiq.

9.14: ninb Raauj yem Hruq Eei ka'naaiq Zauj zwib an ziab txvb Zauj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq yetg Fiag puaq.
9.23: mo-se Zauj aa-lon pia'g wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub. Zwrtq taaib uaq zang, ninb Bua pwav waag pun pc'g fivj. zyruq Eei Favb laavg zyrug hing pun zwavj myenb pwatg.
9.6: mo-se kxvq, “naaiq se zyruq Buaj meib Bua zruj Eei Jauq, zyruq Eei Favb laavg zyrug hing Zwrtq pun meib Bua.”
9.2: ninb kxvq Buaj aa-lon, “meib xij zu'g txb taub vovb kruq txn taaib ziag fi'q zwid yaag txb taub pa'ki yuvb kruq zruj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq. i taub zuvq maiq waaig favj Eei, yaag xij zu'g fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq.
9.20: ninb Bua Yetq Jyenq lx'g Ywav xq kub vwaaig. aa-lon zyrug zx'q Mei an ziab txvb puaq.
9.24: maaib trud yem zyruq Zwrtq taaib puaq yem ziab txvb puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq Zauj yetg zuvq Mei. zwavj myenb pwatg, ninb Bua Fyenb yrub Eei heug cvj Baapq Fiag Tauj Dau.
9.7: mo-se Buaj aa-lon, “taaib fatq teij Tauj ziab txvb Eei Ra'Myen, zx'q meib ziag fi'q zwid Eei ka'naaiq Zauj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq ziag fi'q kanb Eei zwid Zauj pc'g fivj Eei zwid. cvj zx'q tovb pc'g fivj txb taaib fovg hxg ziag Eei ka'naaiq Tevj fi'q ninb Bua Eei zwid ziuj zyruq Buaj Eei waag.”
9.19: vovb Eei Mei Zauj yuvb Eei Mei, Jung Eei tweiq, Zc'g Jaavb Mei, Eutg zeiq Zauj pwav Lan Eei xb Byxvd,
9.17: cvj zx'q yetg Eau fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g an ziab txvb puaq. naaiq yaag maiq funj pia'g Dxmb Dxm puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq.
9.11: ninb zx'q vovb Dopq Zauj xq txb Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Zyavq puaq kwavg.
9.5: ninb Bua zyrug zx'q mo-se Buaj Eei yetg zuvq txb Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg. zwavj myenb kapq zunq taaib fatq Eei, sruq Jyenq zyruq Eei Ra'Myen.
9.9: ninb Eei txn txb vovb Eei Ryaamq taaib pun ninb, ninb zyrug lovg puab Do'q Zo'q Ryaamq zaij Jyenq ziab txvb Eei pyei nxm Jxv. zevg Fiag Eei Ryaamq ninb toj ziab txvb Eei kxn.
9.16: ninb yaag zx'q puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq taaib ei Jyenq leid ziag.
9.4: xij zu'g cvj txb taub vovb Zauj taub pa'ki yuvb kruq taaib ziag pun zyruq, zruj ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq. yaag xij zu'g txb Qruq Jyenq ka'lanq yrub fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g, weig zu'g ib Nxi zyruq xij hing Zwrtq pun meib Bua.’+”
9.10: ninb cvj zx'q ziag fi'q zwid uaq taub scvb Kuq Eei Mei, Zauj Eutg zeiq, Zauj pwav Jyenq Lan Eei xb Byxvd an ziab txvb puaq, ziuj zyruq Buaj mo-se nx.
9.22: aa-lon zyrug Win Jyenq pc'g fivj uaq puv, suv puad pwav waag ninb Bua. ziag liud fi'q zwid Eei ka'naaiq Zauj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq Zauj ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq, aa-lon yem ziab txvb Fiag taaib.
9.12: aa-lon yaag taij puaq ziag uaq taub scvb Kuq. ninb Eei txn txb scvb Kuq Ryaamq pun aa-lon, ninb zyrug Pyetq ziab txvb pyei puv.
9.15: aa-lon cvj zx'q pc'g fivj fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq taaib ziag. ninb zx'q weig fi'q pc'g fivj Eei zwid uaq taub yuvb kruq taij taaib ziag fi'q zwid Navq taaub Rung ziag fi'q zwid uaq nx.
9.13: ninb Bua cvj zx'q puaq ziag Eei scvb Kuq yetg Ganj yetg Ganj, lyemb mGxvq, Zunq pun aa-lon. aa-lon zyrug an ziab txvb kub vwaaig puaq.
9.1: Tauj ta'petq Nxi, mo-se heug aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj myenb koj taaib zunq.

16.18: “aa-lon Zwrtq taaib xij zu'g cvj mivb Tauj yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Eei ziab txvb uaq, weig ziab txvb fi'q zwid. ninb xij zu'g cvj zx'q teij vovb kruq Eei Ryaamq Zauj yuvb Eei Ryaamq zaij pyei puv ziab txvb Eei Jxv.

16.21: ninb zyrug lovg suvb puad maan Jyenq navb uaq taub yuvb Eei mGxvq, Eyemg i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb zruj Hruq vcvg, zruj x'q, Zauj zruj Eei yetg zuvq zwid, an Jyenq yuvb Eei mGxvq. Ga'haaq pun taub Paaiq zyavj Eei myenb taaib txb yuvb mivb puvj uaq teib puvb Waav.
16.14: ninb xij zu'g cvj zx'q teij vovb kruq Eei Ryaamq lovg puab Do'q Tiu Ryaamq mivb kua'q Zeij en Eei weig Ra'Myen, cvj lovg puab Do'q Zo'q Ryaamq Tiu mivb Zeij en Eei weig Ra'Myen mcvj siag Rung.

16.6: “aa-lon xij zu'g zx'q fi'q kanb Eei zwid uaq taub vovb kruq ziag weig fi'q kanb Eei zwid Zauj kanb Eei pyauq zov myenb Eei zwid.
16.34: “naaiq se meib Bua yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid. xij zu'g weig i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei yetg zuvq zwid yetg Havj fi'q yetg Rung.” mo-se zyrug ziuj zyruq Paaiq Eei waag zruj zyavj.
16.2: “xij zu'g Buaj meib Eei kxj, aa-lon, maiq tuvq zanb zang pia'g Bc'g kcvb Dia ka'Euad uaq Qovj, se kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj uaq Qovj,  tovb zyruq Zeij en Eei weig yem lcvd vcvg waag faav kub vwaaig uaq nxm txvj. Riaj ninb zuvq zu'g taig, weig zu'g yia xij yem Bwrnj hing Zwrtq Zeij en Eei weig kub vwaaig.
16.20: “aa-lon weig kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj uaq Qovj Zauj wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub Zauj ziab txvb fi'q liud zwid, ninb xij zu'g zx'q navb Eei uaq taub yuvb fuvj pun zyruq.
16.24: ninb xij zu'g yem nxm Zivb Revg txvj lovg uam Raauj sin cvj zu'q Jyenq yetg kau zu'q Eei sai myenb lwi. Ga'haaq xij zu'g Zwrtq mivb weig kanb yaag weig pc'g fivj zx'q ka'naaiq puaq ziag fi'q kanb Eei zwid Zauj pc'g fivj Eei zwid.
16.28: puaq naaiq teij ka'naaiq uaq taub myenb xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin, Ga'haaq pia'g Dopg liub Zyavq tu'q a'q.
16.7: ninb xij zu'g cvj zx'q uaq teij i taub yuvb kruq yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg fovg hxg pun zyruq.
16.29: “naaiq se meib Bua xij zu'g yetg liud kan Eei leid, mrud Havj Tauj Zyetq Laaj scvb zyepg, meib Bua xij zu'g zei maiq Eang haiq Euvg. yaag maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg kov, maiq kunq pwrnb teig myenb fai yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj Eei kanb fivj myenb,
16.19: yaag lovg puab Do'q Zo'q Ryaamq Tiu mivb ziab txvb siag Rung weig saaj ziab txvb Eei wij, se yem i-saa-laa-en myenb zu'g taaib Eei wij. Navq naaiq zruj, ziab txvb zyrug Zivb Revg mig a'q.
16.17: yem aa-lon pia'g kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj uaq Qovj fi'q zwid Eei zyavb hog, maiq tuvq maaib myenb yem Dopg liub ka'Euad. zuaq Tauj weig kanb, Zauj pyauq zov myenb, Zauj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb fi'q liud zwid Zwrtq taaib.
16.31: naaiq se tivb kov Nxi, xij zu'g hitq Kwrnj. meib Bua xij zu'g lovg Hruq zei maiq Eang haiq Euvg.  se yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid.
16.30: weig zu'g yem naaiq nxm Nxi xij zu'g weig meib Bua fi'q zwid, pun meib Bua Zivb Revg taaib. Navq naaiq, meib Bua zyrug yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Zivb Revg, leib Dutq meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq zwid.
16.27: zruj ziag fi'q zwid Eei vovb kruq Zauj yuvb kruq, tovb aa-lon txb Ryaamq pia'g kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj uaq Qovj fi'q zwid uaq teij scvb Kuq, xij zu'g pyenb Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq. Dopq, xq Zauj Gaiq xij zu'g lovg trud puaq Revg.
16.11: “aa-lon xij zu'g zx'q fi'q kanb Eei zwid uaq taub vovb kruq taij taaib ziag fi'q kanb Eei zwid Zauj pyauq zov myenb Eei zwid.
16.5: xij zu'g yem i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb ka'Euad zx'q Zwrtq i taub yuvb kruq ziag weig fi'q zwid yaag zx'q taub pa'ki yuvb kruq weig puaq ziag.
16.9: aa-lon zyrug zx'q Dxtq penj zyruq Eei pwrng uaq taub yuvb kruq ziag weig fi'q zwid.
16.16: Navq naaig, aa-lon zyrug weig kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj uaq Qovj fi'q zwid, se laaij i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei wij Zauj vcvg zyruq Eei sig yaag laaij ninb Bua Eei yetg zuvq zwid. aa-lon yaag xij zu'g Navq naaiq zruj weig wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub, laaij yem maaib wij Eei pc'g fivj Bu'Dovj.
16.4: xij zu'g zu'q Jyenq la'maab Dia Eei Zivb Revg lwib Daauq yaag zu'q Jyenq la'maab Dia Eei hruj, sai Jyenq Jaaiq Eei la'maab Dia, cvj zx'q la'maab Dia Eei mGxvb peu peu Jyenq mGxvq. naaiq se Zivb Revg Eei lwib hruj zyrug xij zu'g lovg uam Raauj Revg sin Zivj zu'q Jyenq.

16.15: “aa-lon xij zu'g taij weig Tevj zwavj pc'g fivj ziag fi'q zwid uaq taub yuvb, zx'q teij yuvb Ryaamq txb pia'g Bc'g kcvb Dia ka'Euad. ninb xij zu'g Zo'q yuvb Ryaamq Tiu mivb kua'q Zeij en Eei weig kub vwaaig mcvj Zauj Ra'Myen mcvj, Navq lovg vovb kruq Eei Ryaamq zruj uaq nx.
