4.6: sai myenb lovg puab Do'q Zo'q Ryaamq Tiu mivb zyruq Eei Ra'Myen, Zivb Revg Jiaj uaq Qovj Eei Bc'g kcvb Dia Ra'Myen mcvj, siag Rung.
4.34: sai myenb xij zu'g lovg puab Do'q Zo'q teij ziag fi'q zwid naaiq taub pa'ki yuvb txn Eei Ryaamq, zaij puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq Eei ziab txvb pyei nxm kx'q Eei Jxv. zevg Fiag Eei Ryaamq toj Fiag ziab txvb Eei kxn.
4.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘haiq taub Za'g prug zruj txvg haiq Euvg, tovb zyruq hatg maiq pun myenb zruj Eei haiq tiub leid, xij zu'g Navq naaiq zruj.
4.20: naaiq taub vovb ninb xij zu'g Zauj ziag fi'q zwid uaq taub fib Navq Eei zruj. Navq naaiq zruj liud, sai myenb Tevj ninb Bua fi'q zwid. ninb Bua Eei zwid zyrug tu'q kwavg mig a'q.
4.24: xij zu'g txb puad maan Jyenq yuvb Eei mGxvq, yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen, se yem taij puaq ziag scvb Kuq Eei txvj taij. naaiq se ziag fi'q zwid Eei scvb Kuq.
4.28: ninb yetq hiuq tu'q ninb paamd Eei zwid, xij zu'g txb taub maiq waaig favj Eei yuvb Eeid taaib ziag fi'q ninb paamd liud Eei zwid.
4.7: sai myenb xij zu'g cvj zx'q teij Ryaamq zaij yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen, wig pwavb Dopg liub ka'Euad Eei puaq huv tiab pyei nxm kx'q Eei Jxv. zevg Fiag Eei Ryaamq ninb xij zu'g toj Jyenq yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg, puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq Eei ziab txvb kxn.
4.29: xij zu'g txb puad maan Jyenq ziag fi'q zwid naaiq taub yuvb Eeid Eei mGxvq, yem taij puaq ziag Eei scvb Kuq Eei txvj taij.
4.19: ninb yaag xij zu'g zx'q vovb Eei Mei yetg zuvq Zwrtq taaib an ziab txvb puaq.
4.17: zyrug lovg puab Do'q Zo'q Ryaamq Tiu mivb zyruq Eei Ra'Myen, Bc'g kcvb Dia Ra'Myen mcvj, siag Rung.
4.31: ninb xij zu'g zx'q Zwrtq Revg yuvb Eei Mei, Navq zx'q ziag weig Jiu Tov uaq taub scvb Kuq Eei Mei nx. sai myenb zyrug an ziab txvb kub vwaaig puaq, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq. sai myenb Navq naaiq zruj weig Tevj ninb fi'q zwid. ninb Eei zwid zyrug tu'q kwavg liud a'q.
4.30: sai myenb xij zu'g lovg puab Do'q Zo'q teij ziag fi'q zwid naaiq taub yuvb Eei Ryaamq zaij puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq Eei ziab txvb pyei nxm kx'q Eei Jxv. zevg Fiag Eei Ryaamq toj Fiag ziab txvb Eei kxn.
4.27: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub pc'g fivj Za'g prug paamd tovb zyruq hatg maiq tuvq zruj Eei haiq tiub leid, ninb txvg mig a'q.
4.11: mq paag vovb Dopq Zauj yetg zuvq xq, lyemb mGxvq, puab zauj, Jaavb Zauj Gaiq,
4.5: lovg yrub xn zruj sai myenb uaq taub zyrug zx'q teij vovb kruq Eei Ryaamq txb pia'g wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub.
4.9: i nxm Eutg zeiq Zauj peu Eutg zeiq nitq Jaaiq Eei panq yrub. pwav Jyenq Lan Eei xb Byxvd yaag xij zu'g Zauj Eutg zeiq zx'q Zwrtq.
4.16: lovg yrub xn zruj sai myenb uaq taub zyrug txb teij vovb kruq Eei Ryaamq pia'g wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub,
4.4: ninb xij zu'g txb vovb Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg, yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen. txb puad maan Jyenq naaiq taub vovb kruq Eei mGxvq, zyrug yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen taij.
4.10: se Zauj ziag weig Jiu Tov uaq taub vovb fib Navq Eei zx'q Zwrtq Revg. sai myenb zyrug zx'q naaiq pua'q ka'naaiq an puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq Eei ziab txvb puaq.
4.22: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub pyeiq zeiq Za'g prug paamd tovb zyruq, ninb Eei Tinb huvb, hatg maiq tuvq zruj Eei haiq tiub leid, ninb txvg mig a'q.
4.12: se zyavb taub vovb, xij zu'g txb Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq Tauj nxm maiq maaib wij Eei txvj, tovb kwavg saaiq Eei txvj, an Jyenq zaavb kub vwaaig lovg trud puaq. se yem kwavg saaiq uaq nxm txvj puaq.
4.15: zwavj pc'g fivj Eei myenb koj xij zu'g yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen txb puad maan Jyenq naaiq taub vovb kruq Eei mGxvq. yaag xij zu'g yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen taij uaq taub vovb kruq.
4.13: “+‘sij kxvq i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb Za'g prug paamd zwid yaag maiq kx'g Jaav, se paamd zyruq hatg ninb Bua maiq tuvq zruj Eei haiq Euvg leid, ninb Bua txvg mig a'q.
4.26: sai myenb zyrug puaq yetg zuvq Mei Navq puaq ziag weig Jiu Tov uaq taub scvb Kuq Eei Mei nx. sai myenb Navq naaiq zruj weig Tevj ninb fi'q zwid. ninb Eei zwid zyrug tu'q kwavg liud a'q.
4.25: sai myenb xij zu'g lovg puab Do'q Zo'q teij ziag fi'q zwid naaiq taub yuvb Eei Ryaamq zaij puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq Eei ziab txvb pyei nxm kx'q Eei Jxv. zevg Fiag Eei Ryaamq toj Fiag ziab txvb Eei kxn.

10.18: weig zu'g maiq txb scvb Kuq Ryaamq pia'g Zivb Revg Jiaj uaq Qovj ka'Euad, meib Bua hxpg zu'g yem zavg zyruq Eei txvj Eang naaiq taub yuvb Eei xq, ziuj yia Buaj Eei waag.”
10.3: mo-se Buaj aa-lon, “naaiq se zyruq kxvq Eei waag. ninb kxvq, “+‘yem taaib fatq yia uaq teij Bu'Dovj, yia xij piuj mevb yia Zivb Revg. yem zwavj myenb Eei Ra'Myen, zuvq xij pun ninb Bua Taaib yia.’+” aa-lon yaag maiq Ko lo.
10.19: aa-lon tau mo-se, “ib Nxi pc'g fivj txb fovg hxg ziag fi'q zwid Eei ka'naaiq Zauj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen ziag. mq paag ib Nxi yia pwavb Dovg naaiq Eei naang zivb, sij kxvq yia Eang ziag fi'q zwid naaiq teij xq, zyruq haid hxpg Hruq Eei fai?”
10.9: “meib Zauj meib Eei txn Bua pia'g wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub, maiq tuvq hopq a'vung tiuq fai haiq Euvg tiuq. Riaj meib Bua zu'g taig. naaiq se zruj meib Bua txig Jiaj txig yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid.
10.7: meib Bua yaag maiq tuvq leib wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg. maiq zei c'q, meib Bua zu'g taig, weig zu'g zyruq Eei xn myenb yrub yem Jyenq meib Bua mig a'q.” ninb Bua zyrug ei Jyenq mo-se Eei waag zruj.
10.5: ninb Bua zyrug taaib kcv sei, lyemb zu'q Jyenq Eei lwib Daauq, txb Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq ziuj mo-se Buaj Eei waag.
10.16: mo-se zaab naaig Tauj ziag fi'q zwid uaq taub yuvb zyrug hiuq tu'q puaq Revg mig a'q. ninb Qiaj Jiad aa-lon zevg Fiag Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa Zauj i-Taa-maa, zyrug Qa'q naaig ninb Bua,
10.20: mo-se haid liud naaiq teij waag ninb pwavq eij a'q.
10.17: “meib Bua weig haiq tiug maiq yem zavg zyruq Eei txvj Eang? se kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq. naaiq se Jiu pun meib Bua weig pun meib Bua Daam zwavj myenb zruj txvg Eei sig, Tevj ninb Bua fi'q zwid.
10.14: mq paag Zunq kiv Eei lx'g Ywav xq Zauj fovg hxg Eei zwib, meib Zauj meib Eei naamb Erud Jwavg Jyenq Eang tu'q Eei. yaag xij zu'g yem Zivb Revg Eei txvj Eang. naaiq se meib Zauj meib Eei naamb Erud hxpg zu'g tu'q Eei pwrng yem i-saa-laa-en myenb fovg hxg ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq zx'q Zwrtq taaib.
10.4: mo-se heug aa-lon Eei yrub tiaj, utg-si-en, Eei txn, mi-saa-en Zauj en-saa-faan taaib, kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “taaib naaiq maa'b! taaib kcv meib Bua Eei pc'g muab txig Zwrtq zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq, leib Gxi zavg zyruq Eei txvj.”
10.2: zyruq zyrug pun trud Zwrtq taaib puaq ninb Bua, ninb Bua zyrug yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen taig mig a'q.
10.6: mo-se yaag Buaj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa Zauj i-Taa-maa, “maiq tuvq pun meib Bua Eei Ba'pyei fx'q, yaag maiq tuvq petq meib Bua Eei lwib hruj. maiq zei c'q, Riaj meib Bua zu'g taig yaag Riaj zwavj pc'g fivj zu'g zyruq nrud. mq paag meib Bua Eei kxb yrud, se meib Bua Jwavg i-saa-laa-en fivj Eei zwavj myenb, Raub Eyemq zyruq lovg trud puaq taig uaq teij tu'q Eei.
10.13: xij zu'g yem Zivb Revg Eei txvj Eang weig zu'g penj meib Zauj meib Eei txn Bua hxpg zu'g tu'q Eei pwrng, yem lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei ka'naaiq zx'q Zwrtq taaib. naaiq se zyruq Paaiq yia Eei waag.
10.12: mo-se kxvq Buaj aa-lon Zauj ninb zevg Fiag Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa Zauj i-Taa-maa, “zx'q fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g, tovb lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq. zevg Fiag uaq teij, maiq tuvq an pivq yaag xij zu'g yem ziab txvb ka'Len Eang weig zu'g se kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq.
10.15: fovg hxg Eei zaub zwib Zauj Zunq kiv Eei lx'g Ywav xq, xij zu'g Zauj lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei Mei yetg Fiag txb taaib yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Zunq kiv weig zruj Zunq kiv fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. naaiq se meib Zauj meib Eei naamb Erud yetg liud xij zu'g tu'q Eei pwrng, ziuj zyruq Paaiq Eei nx.”
10.11: yaag xij zu'g Faauj i-saa-laa-en myenb hiuq Revg yia lovg mo-se Jiu pun ninb Bua Eei yetg zuvq leib latg.”
10.1: aa-lon Eei txn, naa-Dapg Zauj aa-Bi-hu, kx'g myenb zx'q kx'g myenb Eei huvb lrub taaib, zx'q trud tapq Jyenq, zx'q huv Yetq Jyenq. ninb Bua lovg maiq maaib leid lovg Eei trud fovg hxg zyruq, se maiq ziuj zyruq hatg Eei waag zruj.
10.10: meib Bua hxpg zu'g haib samj tu'q Zwrtq haiq Euvg se Zivb Revg Eei fai Prub Tov Eei ka'naaiq, maaib wij Eei fai maiq maaib wij.

22.18: “xij zu'g Buaj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Zauj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb, ‘ta'faanb meib Bua haiq taub i-saa-laa-en myenb fai yem i-saa-laa-en teib puv Eei kanb fivj myenb, txb ka'naaiq taaib fovg hxg puaq ziag pun zyruq, maiq kunq weig Jaauq suv lcvd Eei vcvg waag fai Zwrtq fim fovg hxg ziag,
22.8: maiq tuvq Eang ninb kanb taig Eei ka'naaiq fai zu'g Yiab zxib vaatg taig Eei ka'naaiq zyrug zu'g maaib wij. yia se zyruq.
22.33: yaag txb meib Bua yem i-yipq teib puv Zwrtq taaib weig zruj meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb uaq taub. yia se zyruq. ”
22.3: “xij zu'g Buaj ninb Bua, ‘txig Jiaj txig, sij kxvq meib Bua Eei haiq taub zeib fun maaib wij Eei zyavb hog taaib fatq i-saa-laa-en myenb fuvj pun zyruq Eei Zivb Revg ka'naaiq, uaq taub xij zu'g Pai kwavg, maiq tu'q yem yia Eei Ra'Myen. yia se zyruq.
22.32: maiq tuvq paaig yia Eei Zivb Revg Buaj. yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj xij zu'g Taaib yia Zivb Revg. yia se zyruq, tovb pun meib Bua Zivb Revg
22.21: haiq taub txb yem vovb kwanb, yuvb kwanb fai pa'ki yuvb kwanb Eei scvb Kuq taaib ziag pun zyruq weig Jiu Tov, fai Jaauq suv lcvd Eei vcvg waag, fai Zwrtq fim fovg hxg, xij zu'g txb maiq waaig favj yaag maiq maaib txvj Gemb Eei scvb Kuq, zyruq Zivj taaib zipq.
22.14: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub Za'g prug Eang fovg hxg Eei Zivb Revg ka'naaiq, ninb xij zu'g Jaauq suv ninb Eang Eei cvj pwib pyaa kruq Eei yetg kruq, yaag zx'q naaiq teij Zivb Revg ka'naaiq fuvj pun sai myenb.
22.23: sij kxvq txb zyavb taaib waaig teij favj fai Eanq Eei vovb fai pa'ki yuvb txn Zwrtq fim ziag tu'q Eei. mq paag sij kxvq ziag weig Jaauq suv lcvd Eei vcvg waag, zyruq maiq zipq.
22.6: haiq taub mua'q zu'g naaiq teij haiq Euvg ka'naaiq zyrug maaib wij Tauj Mwavj. ninb maiq tuvq Eang fovg hxg Eei Zivb Revg ka'naaiq. xij zu'g lovg uam Raauj sin Daavg.
22.2: “xij zu'g Buaj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua, ‘fi'q lovj i-saa-laa-en myenb fuvj pun yia Eei Zivb Revg ka'naaiq, weig maiq paaig yia Eei Zivb Revg Buaj. yia se zyruq. ’
22.20: maiq tuvq txb haiq Euvg waaig favj Eei, weig zu'g zyruq maiq zipq meib Bua Eei.
22.24: maiq tuvq lovg Jaib Dwib faauj Ryaamq Eei, fai Divb Eei, fai ka'naaiq petq zu'g Eei, fai Paaij Jaib Dwib Eei scvb Kuq fovg hxg pun zyruq. yem meib Bua Eei teib puv maiq tuvq Navq naaiq zruj.
22.28: maiq kunq vovb Eeid fai pa'ki yuvb Eeid, maiq tuvq Zauj ninb Eei txn tovb Nxi taij.
22.7: Tauj Ba'Nxi mwrtq Eei zyavb hog ninb Zivb Revg mig a'q. Ga'haaq Eang naaiq teij ka'naaiq tu'q Eei weig zu'g naaiq se ninb Eei Eang hopq.
22.29: “txb ka'naaiq mivb ziag weig lcvd zivb zyruq, xij zu'g zruj hxpg leid weig pun zyruq a'Neiq.
22.19: xij zu'g txb taub maiq waaig favj Eei vovb kruq fai pa'ki yuvb kruq fai yuvb kruq, zyruq Zivj taaib zipq.
22.31: “meib Bua xij zu'g kan lovj yia Buaj Eei waag yaag ei Jyenq zruj. yia se zyruq.
22.30: tovb uaq Nxi xij zu'g Eang Tauj Revg, maiq tuvq lyrub yetg teij Tauj ta'Eeig Dxm. yia se zyruq.
22.27: “vovb fai pa'ki yuvb fai yuvb haiq zang Fiag txn taaib, txn xij zu'g Zauj maa yem siag Nxi. yem ta'petq Nxi faauj mcvj zruj ziag Eei ka'naaiq tu'q Eei, lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq,  zyruq a'Neiq zipq.
22.11: mq paag sij kxvq sai myenb lovg Eaanb maaid nrub fai yem ninb Eei pyauq Zwrtq seij Eei myenb, Eang naaiq teij ka'naaiq tu'q Eei.
22.5: fai mua'q zu'g haiq Euvg Exv Dau haib pun ninb maaib wij Eei ka'naaiq, fai mua'q zu'g haiq taub maiq Zivb Revg Eei myenb maiq kunq uaq taub maaib haiq Euvg wij.
22.9: “+‘sai myenb xij zu'g ei Jyenq yia tivg taaib Eei leib Eeig zruj. maiq zei c'q, Riaj ninb Bua xij zu'g Daam zwid zyrug zu'g taig weig zu'g maiq ei Jyenq naaiq teij leid. yia se zyruq, tovb pun ninb Bua Zivb Revg uaq taub.
22.16: laaij Eang txvg naaiq teij Zivb Revg ka'naaiq, ninb Bua zyrug zu'g Daamb txv tivg zwid. yia se zyruq, tovb pun ninb Bua Zivb Revg uaq taub.’+”
22.4: “+‘ta'faanb aa-lon Eei haiq taub zeib fun putq komb huq pcvg fai sin maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq Eei, ninb maiq tuvq Eang Zivb Revg ka'naaiq. zuaq Tauj ninb Zivb Revg Zivj Eang tu'q. haiq taub mua'q zu'g maaib wij Eei ka'naaiq zyrug maaib wij. se mua'q zu'g Janb taig, fai mua'q zu'g Jaib novg Zwrtq Eei myenb,
22.10: “+‘Kuvj sai myenb Eei Mwavq txig haib Eang fovg hxg Eei Zivb Revg ka'naaiq. kanb taub maiq Kub Eang. tivb sai myenb Eei pyauq Eei Kc'q myenb fai Zivq taaib Eei kovb myenb maiq Kub Eang.
22.22: maiq tuvq txb mziv mcvb Eei, zu'g mun syav Eei, puab zauj waaig Eei, maaib ka'naaiq lyrug Zwrtq Eei, putq faav putq laaij Eei scvb Kuq fovg hxg pun zyruq. maiq tuvq zx'q naaiq teij haiq Euvg an ziab txvb lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq.
22.12: sij kxvq sai myenb Eei sia'q txv Jaa, maiq zeid lovg zruj sai Eei myenb, ninb maiq Kub Eang fovg hxg Eei Zivb Revg ka'naaiq.
22.15: sai myenb maiq tuvq pun i-saa-laa-en myenb fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei Zivb Revg ka'naaiq maaib wij.
22.13: mq paag sij kxvq sai myenb Eei sia'q kwaaq mivb fai leib mivb yaag maiq maaib fu'Jweiq, cvj Rwrnj taaib yem ninb Eei tia Eei pyauq Navq lunj Eei zyavb hog nx, zyrug Eang ninb Eei tia Eei Eang hopq tu'q Eei. mq paag ka'Eiag Eei myenb maiq Kub Eang.
22.25: yaag maiq tuvq lovg yem Janj tu'q taaib Eei naaiq pua'q scvb Kuq fovg hxg zruj meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei Eang hopq. naaiq Euvg scvb Kuq waaig favj, maaib txvj Gemb Eei, zyruq zyrug maiq zipq.’+”

12.3: Tauj ta'petq uaq Nxi, xij zu'g Tevj uaq taub kub vwaab txn Jiaj kaatq Eei leid.
12.8: sij kxvq ninb maiq maaib Eaanb maaid yetg taub pa'ki yuvb txn, ninb xij zu'g txb i nxm nx'g Go fai i nxm pc'g kopq lunj. lovg nxm zruj puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. cvj lovg nxm fi'q zwid, pun sai myenb Tevj ninb saaj wij. ninb zyrug Zivb Revg mig a'q.’+”
12.4: msia'q txn Zxg xij zu'g cvj zuaq faab zyepg faam Nxi Zivj taaib haib saaj Revg yuvd kub vwaad Zwrtq Ryaamq Eei wij. ninb yaag maiq tuvq mua'q zu'g haiq Euvg Zivb Revg Eei ka'naaiq. yaag maiq tuvq pia'g zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub. zuaq Tauj yuvd kub vwaad Zwrtq Ryaamq maaib wij Eei Nxib Eia'g pwavq.
12.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘sij kxvq haiq taub msia'q txn maaib kub vwaad, yuvd tu'q taub txn, uaq taub msia'q txn maaib wij siag Nxi Navq sinb yeng Eei Nxib Eia'g maaib wij uaq nx.
12.6: “+‘Tauj saaj wij Eei Nxib Eia'g pwavq, maiq kunq yuvd tu'q txn fai sia'q, ninb xij zu'g txb taub txij Havj Eei pa'ki yuvb txn zruj puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. yaag xij zu'g txb nxm pc'g kopq lunj fai yetg nxm nx'g Go ziag weig fi'q zwid. xij zu'g txb Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg Jiu pun sai myenb.
12.5: mq paag yuvd tu'q kub vwaab sia'q nx, zyrug maaib wij i nxm leib paaij, Navq sinb yeng Eei Nxib Eia'g maaib wij uaq nx. xij zu'g cvj zuaq lua'g zyepg lua'g Nxi Tauj yuvd kub vwaad Zwrtq Ryaamq maaib wij Eei Nxib Eia'g pwavq.
12.7: sai myenb zyrug txb naaiq teij ka'naaiq yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen ziag Tevj ninb saaj Revg yuvd kub vwaad Zwrtq Ryaamq Eei wij. naaiq se msia'q txn yuvd kub vwaad Eei leid maiq kunq yuvd txn fai sia'q.

15.18: mJavg msia'q Zauj liud txig yaag maaib Jaib novg Zwrtq, i taub zuvq xij zu'g lovg uam Raauj sin yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.8: “+‘haiq taub lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq Eei myenb Twiq uamb Rwib nctq zu'g myenb, uaq taub myenb xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin, yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.33: yaag weig msia'q txn maaib sinb yeng Eei zyavb hog zyrug maaib wij, yaag weig mJavg txn fai msia'q txn lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq, yaag weig mJavg txn Zauj maaib wij Eei msia'q txn nitq txig.
15.3: maiq kunq naaiq teij ka'naaiq Zwrtq fai zc'q Jyenq ka'Euad, Zxg pun uaq laanb myenb maaib wij. naaiq se lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq pun myenb maaib wij Eei leid.
15.32: naaiq teij leid se weig mJavg txn lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq fai Jaib novg Zwrtq zyrug pun ninb maaib wij,
15.21: haiq taub mua'q zu'g ninb Eei Zruj, uaq taub xij zu'g Roj kanb Eei lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin, yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.14: Tauj ta'petq Nxi xij zu'g txb i nxm nx'g Go fai i nxm pc'g kopq lunj, yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen, wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg Jiu pun sai myenb.
15.23: maiq kunq ninb zweid Zruj fai haiq Euvg ka'naaiq, haiq taub mua'q zu'g zyrug maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.6: haiq taub zweid zu'g ninb zweid Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq, uaq taub xij zu'g Roj kanb Eei lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin, yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘haiq taub mJavg txn lamb Bweid txvj Zwrtq maiq hxpg zu'g Zwrtq Eei ka'naaiq, uaq teij ka'naaiq maaib wij.
15.20: “+‘ninb maaib sinb yeng Eei zyavb hog pweij haiq nxm txvj, uaq nxm txvj maaib wij. ninb zweid haiq Euvg ka'naaiq, uaq Euvg ka'naaiq zyrug maaib wij.
15.24: “+‘sij kxvq haiq taub mJavg txn Zauj maaib sinb yeng Eei msia'q txn nitq txig, mJavg txn zyrug zu'g msia'q txn Eei wij kua'q ninb, ninb zyrug maaib wij siag Nxi. ninb pweij Eei haiq zuv Zruj yaag maaib wij.
15.28: “+‘mq paag sij kxvq ninb Zwrtq Eei Ryaamq tivb Revg, xij zu'g cvj zuaq siag Nxi. Ga'haaq ninb maiq maaib wij.
15.7: “+‘haiq taub mua'q lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq Eei mJavg txn xij zu'g Roj kanb Eei lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin, yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.29: Tauj ta'petq Nxi ninb xij zu'g txb i nxm nx'g Go fai i nxm pc'g kopq lunj Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg, Jiu pun sai myenb.
15.19: “+‘msia'q txn Laab Laaj maaib sinb yeng Eei zyavb hog, ninb maaib wij siag Nxi. haiq taub mua'q zu'g ninb, uaq taub zyrug maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.17: lwib hruj fai haiq Euvg lovg Dopq zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq maaib Jaib novg kua'q zu'g, xij zu'g lovg uam Raauj yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.31: “+‘meib Bua xij zu'g Navq naaiq pun i-saa-laa-en myenb simq Gxi ninb Bua Eei wij. Riaj ninb Bua txb wij taaib kua'q zu'g yia Eei Dopg liub, tovb yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj Eei txvj. ninb Bua zyrug laaij ninb Bua kanb Eei wij zu'g taig.’+”
15.30: sai myenb zyrug lovg nxm ziag weig fi'q zwid, lovg nxm puaq ziag. ninb Navq naaiq nx Tevj maaib Ryaamq Zwrtq uaq taub msia'q txn fi'q zwid.
15.27: haiq taub mua'q zu'g uaq teij ka'naaiq zyrug maaib wij. xij zu'g Roj kanb Eei lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.11: “+‘haiq taub myenb lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq yaag maiq lovg uam Raauj puad Daavg, ninb mua'q zu'g haiq taub, uaq taub xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin, yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.5: haiq taub mua'q zu'g ninb Eei Zruj, uaq taub xij zu'g Roj kanb Eei lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin, yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.9: “+‘lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq Eei myenb zweid Jiaj Eei maab xn fai haiq Euvg ka'naaiq, uaq Euvg zyrug maaib wij.
15.16: “+‘haiq taub mJavg txn maaib Jaib novg Zwrtq, uaq taub xij zu'g lovg uam Raauj Revg zyavb sin. ninb yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.4: “+‘haiq taub mJavg txn lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq cvj pweij haiq zuv Zruj, uaq zuv Zruj zyrug maaib wij. zweid haiq nxm ka'naaiq, uaq nxm ka'naaiq yaag maaib wij.
15.10: haiq taub mua'q zu'g naaiq teij keb Jiaj zweid Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq, uaq taub maaib wij Tauj Mwavj. haiq taub Tevj zx'q naaiq teij zweid Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin, yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.22: haiq taub mua'q zu'g ninb zweid Eei ka'naaiq, uaq taub xij zu'g Roj kanb Eei lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin, yaag maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
15.12: “+‘haiq taub myenb lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq cvj mua'q zu'g niab mx, xij zu'g Bx'q niab mx kwavg. sij kxvq mua'q zu'g lovg Dyavj zruj taaib Eei Jaab sig, xij zu'g lovg uam Raauj.
15.15: sai myenb zyrug Tevj ninb ziag. ninb lovg nxm ziag fi'q zwid, cvj lovg nxm puaq ziag. ninb Navq naaiq nx yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Tevj lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq uaq laanb myenb fi'q zwid.
15.13: “+‘lamb Bweid txvj maaib ka'naaiq Zwrtq Eei myenb lovj mivb, Zxg xij zu'g zuaq siag Nxi Zivj tu'q saaj wij. ninb xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj, lovg uamb taaib Raauj sin, ninb zyrug Zivb Revg mig a'q.
15.1: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon,
15.26: maaib Ryaamq Zwrtq Eei zyavb hog, ninb pweij Eei haiq zuv Zruj fai zweid Eei haiq Euvg ka'naaiq zyrug maaib wij, Navq sinb yeng Eei zyavb hog maaib wij uaq nx.
15.25: “+‘haiq taub msia'q txn maaib Ryaamq Zwrtq Zamb Nxi, maiq txij sinb yeng Eei zyavb hog, fai kaub laub sinb yeng Eei zyavb hog, ta'faanb Zxg maaib Ryaamq Zwrtq Eei Nxib Eia'g maaib wij, Navq sinb yeng Eei zyavb hog uaq nx.

13.18: “sij kxvq maaib myenb zyavb zweib lovj mivb,
13.45: “myenb putq komb huq pcvg xij zu'g zu'q petq huq Eei lwib hruj, puvj Ba'pyei fx'q, pwav Jyenq kub vwaaig uaq mcvj Rwib meij, yaag heug Jyenq kxvq, ‘maaib wij, maaib wij a'q.’
13.3: sai myenb zyrug zaab mavg Dopq penj pcvg uaq nxm txvj. pwatg uaq nxm txvj Eei pyei pc'g mig a'q, yaag pwatg pcvg maiq taan yem Dopq Navq, se pia'g Do Eei, zyrug funj penj komb huq pcvg. sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb maaib wij a'q.
13.43: sai myenb xij zu'g zaab mavg. sij kxvq pwatg yem mGxvq fai pyxvb omj Eei txvj pc'g si'q Navq komb huq pcvg nx,
13.50: sai myenb mavg liud zyrug kanb Za'levg Yetq Jyenq yetg nxm txvj siag Nxi.
13.14: mq paag sij kxvq maaib xb lunj si'q putq Zwrtq haiq nxm txvj, ninb maaib wij a'q.
13.48: se lovg la'maab swij fai pa'ki swij Datq taaib fai Zi'q taaib Eei lwib hruj, fai scvb Kuq Dopq fai lovg scvb Kuq Dopq zruj taaib Eei haiq Euvg ka'naaiq,
13.34: ta'Zyetq Nxi sai myenb xij zu'g zaab mavg putq faav syetq Eei txvj. sij kxvq pwatg Dopq maiq putq Javq Jyenq mivb nx, yaag Kuvj yem Dopq Navq, maiq pia'g Do, sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb maiq maaib wij. ninb xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj zyrug maiq maaib wij a'q.
13.2: “sij kxvq haiq taub pwatg Dopq omj, fai Dopq huq, fai Navq trud puaq laaud nx, Riaj penj komb huq pcvg. xij zu'g txb mivb Tauj aa-lon sai myenb fai aa-lon Eei zeib fun yetg taub sai myenb.
13.36: xij zu'g pun sai myenb zaab mavg ninb. sij kxvq pwatg putq faav syetq Eei txvj yem Dopq putq Javq Jyenq mivb, sai myenb maiq zu'g lxd pyei yavb. ninb zuvq maaib wij a'q.
13.35: sij kxvq ninb saaj liud wij mq paag Ga'haaq putq faav syetq Eei txvj putq Javq Jyenq mivb,
13.24: “haiq taub zu'g trud puaq, yem zu'g puaq uaq nxm txvj pwatg xb lunj Zwrtq pc'g si'q fai pc'g,
13.7: ninb tu'q sai myenb tivg ninb Zivb Revg Eei mq paag sij kxvq Ga'haaq pwatg Dopq cvj Jaa huq Jyenq mivb, xij zu'g cvj mivb pun sai myenb mavg.
13.17: sai myenb xij zu'g zaab mavg. pwatg uaq teij txvj Twij setq pc'g, sai myenb zyrug tivg uaq laanb myenb se Zivb Revg Eei. ninb zyrug Zivb Revg mig a'q.
13.58: mq paag sij kxvq Roj liud naaiq teij lwib hruj, fai Datq taaib, Zi'q taaib Eei Dia, fai lovg Dopq zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq, yaag pwatg Jiaj Buaq Eei txvj Eei setq Twij Revg nx, xij zu'g cvj Roj Rung. naaiq teij ka'naaiq zyrug Zivb Revg.”
13.49: yaag sij kxvq naaiq teij lwib hruj fai lovg Dopq zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq Jiaj Buaq taaib mcv Eei fai si'q Eei, naaiq Euvg ka'naaib Buaq se haib putq Jyenq mivb. zuvq xij zu'g pun sai myenb zaab mavg.
13.11: pun Ziv maiq haib lovj, penj yem Dopq Eei komb huq pcvg. sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb maaib wij a'q. maiq tuvq Kwrnj ninb a'q, weig zu'g ninb zuvq maaib wij mig a'q.
13.33: naaiq taub myenb xij zu'g Teij Ba'pyei fai syaam. mq paag putq faav Eei txvj maiq tuvq Teij. sai myenb zyrug cvj Kwrnj Jyenq siag Nxi.
13.16: sij kxvq naaiq teij xb lunj Twij setq pc'g Revg, ninb xij zu'g cvj mivb lxd sai myenb.
13.40: “sij kxvq haiq taub mJavg txn Eei Ba'pyei pyob, ninb se mGxvq Fav Eei mq paag Zivb Revg, maiq maaib wij.
13.59: naaiq se ka'naaiq Jiaj Buaq Eei leid weig tivg ka'naaiq se Zivb Revg fai maaib wij, maiq kunq se lovg pa'ki swij fai la'maab Dia Eei lwib hruj, Datq taaib, Zi'q taaib Eei Dia, fai lovg scvb Kuq Dopq zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq.
13.37: mq paag ziuj sai myenb mavg pwatg putq faav syetq Eei txvj maiq Jaa putq, yem faav ka'Euad yaag Zwrtq pyei Jia'q nx, putq faav Eei txvj se lovj mig a'q. uaq taub myenb yaag maiq maaib wij. sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb Zivb Revg mig a'q.
13.4: mq paag pwatg uaq nxm txvj pc'g yaag Navq Kuvj yem Dopq penj Navq, uaq nxm txvj Eei pyei yaag maiq pc'g nx, sai myenb zyrug Kwrnj Jyenq putq pcvg uaq taub kanb yem nxm txvj siag Nxi.
13.51: Tauj ta'Zyetq Nxi, sai myenb cvj zaab mavg. pwatg naaiq teij ka'naaib Buaq cvj putq Jyenq mivb, maiq kunq yem lwib hruj fai Datq taaib fai Zi'q taaib Eei ka'naaiq, fai haiq Euvg lovg Dopq zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq, naaiq Euvg ka'naaib Buaq se to'g Eei. naaiq teij Jiaj Buaq Eei ka'naaiq zyrug maaib wij.
13.12: “sij kxvq Dopq Eei pcvg putq kxmj sin, ziuj sai myenb pwatg se yem mGxvq Fiag Tauj zauj,
13.46: ta'faanb putq Jyenq uaq Euvg pcvg, ninb maaib wij a'q. ninb xij zu'g mivb yem ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq, yaag xij zu'g Du'g taub kanb yem Navq.
13.13: sai myenb xij zu'g zaab mavg. pwatg pcvg pwavq Revg zyavb sin, yem mGxvq Tauj zauj, zyrug tivg ninb Zivb Revg mig a'q. weig zu'g zyavb sin pc'g Revg ninb zyrug Zivb Revg mig a'q.
13.26: mq paag sij kxvq sai myenb zaab mavg, pwatg uaq nxm txvj Eei pyei maiq pc'g, pwatg maiq Do, Kuvj Dopq penj Navq, yaag pwatg mitg teij, sai myenb zyrug Kwrnj Jyenq pun pcvg myenb kanb yem nxm txvj siag Nxi.
13.28: mq paag sij kxvq pwatg uaq nxm txvj mtaaib Navq lod uaq nx, yaag maiq huq Jyenq kan Dopq mivb, yaag mitg teij Eei, se omj laaij zu'g trud puaq Navq, sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb maiq maaib wij. se Kuvj trud puaq Eei naanj Navq.
13.54: sai myenb xij zu'g hatg Roj Jiaj Buaq Eei ka'naaiq. Roj liud, xij zu'g cvj an Jyenq uaq siag Nxi.
13.8: sai myenb zaab liud, pwatg Jaa putq Javq Jyenq mivb, sai myenb zyrug tivg Dopq huq uaq taub myenb maaib wij. se komb huq pcvg a'q.
13.9: “sij kxvq maaib haiq taub putq komb huq pcvg, xij zu'g txb mivb sai myenb uaq.
13.32: Tauj ta'Zyetq Nxi, sai myenb cvj mavg putq faav Eei txvj. pwatg syetq Eei txvj maiq Jaa huq mivb, yem faav ka'Euad maiq maaib Ba'pyei yavb, yaag pwatg Navq Kuvj yem Dopq penj Navq, maiq pia'g Do,
13.21: mq paag sij kxvq sai myenb zaab mavg Eei zyavb hog pwatg uaq nxm txvj Eei pyei maiq pc'g, Kuvj Dopq penj Navq, maiq pia'g Do, yaag pwatg mitg teij a'q, sai myenb zyrug Kwrnj Jyenq uaq laanb myenb, pun ninb kanb yem nxm txvj siag Nxi.
13.57: mq paag sij kxvq Ga'haaq naaiq teij lwib hruj, fai Datq taaib, Zi'q taaib Eei Dia, fai lovg Dopq zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq, Zxg cvj Jiaj Buaq, pwatg putq Zamq Jyenq faauj, xij zu'g lovg trud puaq kwavg.
13.23: mq paag sij kxvq pwatg uaq nxm txvj Navq lod nx, maiq putq Javq Jyenq mivb, se zweib Eei naanj Navq. sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb maiq maaib wij.
13.6: Tauj ta'Zyetq Nxi, sai myenb cvj zaab Rung. pwatg uaq nxm txvj mitg teij, maiq Jaa putq nx, sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb Zivb Revg, Kuvj Zwrtq teij paaq ka'naaiq Navq. ninb xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj zyrug Zivb Revg mig a'q.
13.55: Roj liud, sij kxvq pwatg naaiq teij ka'naaiq maiq Twij setq, maiq kunq maiq putq Javq Jyenq mivb, Zxg maaib wij. maiq kunq Jiaj Buaq ka'Euad fai ka'Eiag mcvj, xij zu'g lovg trud puaq kwavg.
13.44: uaq taub myenb zyrug maaib komb huq pcvg. ninb maaib wij a'q. sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb maaib wij, weig zu'g pcvg putq Zwrtq yem ninb Eei mGxvq.
13.20: sai myenb zaab mavg pwatg putq uaq nxm txvj maiq taan yem Dopq Navq, se pia'g Do Eei, uaq nxm txvj Eei pyei yaag Twij setq pc'g Revg mig a'q, sai myenb zyrug tivg uaq laanb myenb maaib wij. se penj komb huq pcvg yem zyavb Jiaj zweib Eei txvj Zwrtq.
13.5: Tauj ta'Zyetq Nxi, sai myenb cvj zaab ninb. sij kxvq ziuj sai myenb pwatg, Dopq maiq kanb Euvg, maiq Jaa putq nx, sai myenb zyrug cvj Kwrnj Jyenq siag Nxi.
13.56: sij kxvq Roj liud, sai myenb cvj zaab mavg uaq zang pwatg Jiaj Buaq Eei txvj Eei setq Twij nx, xij zu'g petq Jiaj Buaq Eei txvj Zwrtq uaq teij lwib hruj fai Dopq fai Datq taaib, Zi'q taaib Eei Dia.
13.53: “mq paag sai myenb zaab mavg Eei zyavb hog, sij kxvq pwatg yem Datq taaib fai Zi'q taaib Eei lwib hruj fai lovg Dopq zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq, Jiaj naaiq Euvg Buaq maiq putq Javq Jyenq mivb,
13.19: Ga'haaq yem zyavb Jiaj zweib Eei txvj omj taaib pc'g Eei fai maaib teij txvj pc'g si'q, ninb xij zu'g mivb pun sai myenb mavg.
13.38: “maiq kunq mJavg msia'q, sij kxvq sin zavg Eei Dopq pc'g mivb yetg tyemq yetg tyemq Eei,
13.31: sij kxvq sai myenb zaab mavg pwatg putq faav syetq Eei txvj maiq Do, Kuvj yem Dopq Navq, yaag maiq maaib Ba'pyei fai syaam Jia'q yem uaq nxm txvj, sai myenb zyrug Kwrnj Jyenq uaq laanb myenb pun ninb kanb yem nxm txvj siag Nxi.
13.52: sai myenb xij zu'g puaq kwavg Revg naaiq teij lovg pa'ki swij fai la'maab Dia Datq taaib Eei lwib hruj fai lovg Dopq zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq, weig zu'g naaiq Euvg ka'naaib Buaq se to'g Eei. xij zu'g lovg trud puaq kwavg.
13.27: Tauj ta'Zyetq Nxi, sai myenb xij zu'g cvj zaab Rung ninb. sij kxvq pwatg huq Jyenq kan Dopq mivb, sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb maaib wij, se komb huq pcvg.
13.41: haiq taub Eei pyxvb Zeiq Zauj mGxvq Ra'Myen mcvj Eei Ba'pyei pyob, ninb Eei mGxvq Fav Eei mq paag ninb Zivb Revg, maiq maaib wij.
13.1: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon,
13.39: sai myenb xij zu'g zaab mavg. sij kxvq pwatg uaq nxm txvj Kuvj pc'g Navq, maiq yrug nx, uaq taub myenb se Zivb Revg Eei, maiq maaib wij.
13.47: “sij kxvq lwib hruj Jiaj Buaq, maiq kunq pa'ki yuvb pyei fai la'maab Dia Eei lwib hruj,
13.10: sai myenb zyrug zaab mavg. pwatg Dopq pc'g yaag omj, pun uaq nxm txvj Eei pyei pc'g, omj Eei txvj yaag Tov, Zwrtq xb si'q,
13.25: sai myenb xij zu'g zaab mavg. pwatg uaq nxm txvj Eei pyei Twij setq pc'g Revg, yaag pwatg maiq taan yem Dopq Navq, se pia'g Do Eei, se komb huq pcvg yem trud puaq Eei txvj Zwrtq. sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb maaib wij. penj komb huq pcvg a'q.
13.22: pwatg Dopq cvj putq Javq Jyenq mivb nx, sai myenb zyrug tivg ninb maaib wij. se haib Jiaj myenb Eei pcvg.
13.42: mq paag sij kxvq mGxvq fai pyxvb Fav Zwrtq teij pc'g si'q Eei txvj, naaiq se yem mGxvq Fav fai pyxvb Zwrtq Eei komb huq pcvg.
13.15: sai myenb zaab mavg, pwatg xb lunj si'q putq Zwrtq, zyrug tivg ninb maaib wij. uaq teij xb lunj maaib wij. se komb huq pcvg a'q.
13.29: “maiq kunq mJavg fai msia'q, haiq taub putq faav yem mGxvq fai haab paab,

25.8: “+‘meib Bua xij zu'g saauq siag nxm tivb kov Havj, se saauq siag Havj siag Rung. yetg zuvq se feij zyepg Juaq Havj.

25.38: yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, tovb txb meib Bua yem i-yipq teib puv Zwrtq taaib weig zx'q Kaa-naa-an teib puv Jiu pun meib Bua yaag zruj meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb uaq taub.

25.47: “+‘sij kxvq yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj maaib taub kanb fivj myenb fai taaib zyrug meib Bua yem Eei myenb putq zxib Jiad taaib, cvj maaib taub meib Bua Eei kxb yrud Jomg Fiag zyrug maaig kanb zruj nrub Tevj uaq taub kanb fivj myenb fai zyrug meib Bua uaq taub fai yetg taub ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng myenb,

25.25: “+‘sij kxvq maaib taub meib Bua Eei kxb yrud Jomg Fiag zyrug maaig teij ninb Eei Dau, ninb kaub Zyen Jiaj uaq taub Zyenb Ze'q xij zu'g taaib zua'g ninb Eei kxb yrud maaig Eei Dau Rwrnj.

25.29: “+‘sij kxvq myenb maaig pyauq yem maaib zivb laatg Eei zivb, maaig liud taaub Havj ninb zua'g Rwrnj tu'q Eei. yem yetg Havj ka'Euad Zxg maaib leid zua'g Rwrnj.
